%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22NSA%20Ajit%20Doval%20Visits%20Israel%2C%20Meets%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12082209%2FGIZ-_OEWoAA9CVV.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20the%20first%20high-level%20visit%20to%20Israel%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Gaza%20war%20last%20October%2C%20Indian%20national%20security%20advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%20met%20with%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20on%20Monday%20and%20discussed%20the%20ongoing%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20side%20did%20not%20officially%20announce%20the%20visit%2C%20with%20news%20of%20the%20meeting%20emerging%20from%20the%20Israeli%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20late%20on%20Monday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20account%20of%20the%20discussion%2C%20as%20shared%20on%20X%2C%20highlighted%20that%20the%20primary%20topic%20was%20the%20ongoing%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPrime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20met%20today%20with%20Indian%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%20and%20updated%20him%20on%20recent%20developments%20in%20the%20fighting%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20The%20sides%20also%20discussed%20the%20effort%20to%20release%20the%20hostages%20and%20the%20issue%20of%20humanitarian%20assistance%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20prime%20minister%20has%20had%20several%20phone%20calls%20with%20the%20Israeli%20prime%20minister%20and%20Palestinian%20president%2C%20but%20this%20is%20the%20first%20visit%20by%20a%20senior%20Indian%20official%20in%20the%20last%20five%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20was%20also%20attended%20by%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20top%20aides%2C%20director%20of%20the%20national%20security%20council%2C%20foreign%20policy%20advisor%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Indian%20ambassador%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImmediately%20after%20Hamas%20launched%20a%20terror%20attack%20on%20October%207%2C%20the%20Indian%20prime%20minister%20had%20solely%20expressed%20solidarity%20with%20Israel.%20More%20than%201%2C200%20Israeli%20and%20foreign%20citizens%20were%20killed%20and%20250%20taken%20hostage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20operation%2C%20which%20began%20with%20aerial%20bombing%2C%20followed%20by%20ground%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%20strip%2C%20has%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%20over%2030%2C000%20people%2C%20including%2025%2C000%20women%20and%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20deaths%20in%20Gaza%20became%20evident%2C%20India%20nuanced%20its%20position%20on%20the%20crisis%20by%20asserting%20that%20while%20terrorism%20was%20unacceptable%2C%20humanitarian%20aid%20had%20to%20be%20given%20at%20the%20earliest%20and%20reiterated%20traditional%20support%20for%20the%20two-state%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20December%202023%20resolution%20in%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20which%20called%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710212025000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12082209%2FGIZ-_OEWoAA9CVV.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnsa-ajit-doval-visits-israel-meets-benjamin-netanyahu%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Israeli%20account%20of%20the%20discussion%2C%20as%20shared%20on%20X%2C%20highlighted%20that%20the%20primary%20topic%20was%20the%20ongoing%20violence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnsa-ajit-doval-visits-israel-meets-benjamin-netanyahu%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Sayonara%20Jimmy'%3A%20Boycott%20calls%20for%20England%20to%20plan%20beyond%20Anderson%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710211297000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108418