ame%20changer%20in%20southeast%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20this%20weapon%20would%20mean%20for%20India's%20nuclear%20and%20missile%20programme%2C%20Dr%20Saraswat%20told%20NDTV%20that%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bforce%20multiplier%26quot%3B%20it%20would%20increase%20the%20weapon's%20%26quot%3Bradius%20of%20influence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20weapon%20system%20is%20based%20on%20Multiple%20Independently%20Targetable%20Re-entry%20Vehicle%20(MIRV)%20technology%2C%20which%20means%20a%20single%20missile%20can%20deploy%20multiple%20nuclear%20warheads%20and%20hit%20targets%20at%20different%20locations%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20create%20a%20much%20better%20annihilation%20even%20with%20one%20missile.%20The%20number%20of%20missiles%20that%20will%20be%20required%20to%20be%20launched%20in%20future%20against%20an%20enemy%20attack%20would%20be%20fewer.%20This%20is%20called%20Force%20Multiplier%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Saraswat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20he%20added%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20major%20technology%20in%20terms%20of%20missile%20technology%2C%20control%2C%20guidance%2C%20precision%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Agni-5%20MIRV%20uses%20smaller%20size%20warheads%20to%20generate%20a%20greater%20effect.%20Dr%20Saraswat%20called%20it%20an%20%26quot%3Bevolutionary%20process%26quot%3B%20of%20nuclear%20technology%20in%20which%20India%20is%20%26quot%3Bnowhere%20behind%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20successful%20test%20of%20Agni-5%20MIRV%20was%20applauded%20this%20evening%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bproud%20of%20our%20DRDO%20scientists%20for%20Mission%20Divyastra%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProud%20of%20our%20DRDO%20scientists%20for%20Mission%20Divyastra%2C%20the%20first%20flight%20test%20of%20indigenously%20developed%20Agni-5%20missile%20with%20Multiple%20Independently%20Targetable%20Re-entry%20Vehicle%20(MIRV)%20technology%2C'%20PM%20Modi%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20of%20India%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20said%20it%20was%20an%20'important%20milestone%20in%20India's%20march%20towards%20greater%20geo-strategic%20role%20and%20capabilities%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20is%20currently%20possessed%20by%20a%20handful%20of%20nations%20including%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20Russia%2C%20France%2C%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710205800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fe726s1b_agni5-mirv-_625x300_11_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-drdo-chief-on-agni-5-mirv-gives-india-next-level-deterrence-capability-5220771%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Agni-5%20MIRV%2C%20the%20landmark%20ballistic%20weapons%20system%2C%20takes%20India's%20second-strike%20capability%20to%20the%20next%20level%2C%20giving%20it%20%26quot%3Bhigher%20potency%2C%20better%20influence%20and%20denser%20zone%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20V%20K%20Saraswat%2C%20former%20Director%20General%20of%20DRDO.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-drdo-chief-on-agni-5-mirv-gives-india-next-level-deterrence-capability-5220771%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-drdo-chief-on-agni-5-mirv-gives-india-next-level-deterrence-capability-5220771%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-drdo-chief-on-agni-5-mirv-gives-india-next-level-deterrence-capability-5220771%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20May%20Skip%20Lok%20Sabha%20Contest%2C%20Unease%20In%20Party%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20may%20not%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20this%20time%20--%20a%20possibility%20that%20has%20rung%20alarm%20bells%20in%20some%20sections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20general%20cannot%20be%20missing%20in%20the%20battlefield%20is%20the%20sentiment%20and%20they%20advocate%20him%20leading%20from%20the%20front.%20But%20the%20party%20veteran%20has%20pointed%20out%20a%20crucial%20aspect%20--%20the%20chief%20needs%20to%20take%20care%20the%20big%20picture%20without%20getting%20involved%20in%20his%20own%20personal%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20was%20the%20one%20unanimous%20name%20in%20the%20candidates'%20list%20for%20Karnataka%20that%20was%20discussed%20last%20week%20for%20the%20Gulbarga%20constituency.%20But%20he%20is%20likely%20to%20nominate%20his%20son-in-law%20Radhakrishnan%20Doddamani%2C%20sources%20close%20to%20him%20have%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20had%20won%20twice%20from%20the%20Gulbarga%20constituency%20but%20lost%20in%202019.%20He%20has%20since%20been%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20where%20he%20is%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition.%20He%20has%20four%20more%20years%20left%20in%20the%20Upper%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge's%20son%20Priyank%20Kharge%20is%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20cabinet%20of%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah.%20Reports%20say%20he%20is%20not%20keen%20on%20contesting%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20The%20Congress%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20is%20refraining%20from%20poaching%20state%20ministers%20for%20the%20general%20election%20-%20only%20one%20minister%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20has%20said%20he%20does%20not%20want%20to%20get%20%26quot%3Bconfined%20to%20one%20constituency%20but%20concentrate%20across%20the%20country%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20no%20record%20of%20party%20chiefs%20not%20contesting%20elections.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20both%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20have%20contested%20and%20won%2C%20though%20Mr%20Gandhi%20lost%20party%20bastion%20Smriti%20Irani%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20the%20BJP%2C%20while%20JP%20Nadda%20is%20not%20contesting%20this%20year%2C%20in%202014%20and%202019%2C%20then%20BJP%20chiefs%20Rajnath%20Singh%20and%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20won%20huge%20victories%20from%20Lucknow%20and%20Gandhinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20meeting%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20was%20projected%20by%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20her%20Delhi%20counterpart%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20as%20the%20Prime%20Ministerial%20face%20of%20the%20Opposition%20bloc.%20But%20Mr%20Kharge%20had%20declined%2C%20saying%20the%20matter%20should%20be%20discussed%20once%20the%20elections%20are%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710205500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fqqbeckr_mallikarjun-kharge_625x300_28_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmallikarjun-kharge-may-skip-lok-sabha-contest-unease-in-party-sources-5221805%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20may%20not%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20this%20time%20--%20a%20possibility%20that%20has%20rung%20alarm%20bells%20in%20some%20sections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmallikarjun-kharge-may-skip-lok-sabha-contest-unease-in-party-sources-5221805%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Is%20Aseefa%20Bhutto%2C%20Pak%20President's%20Daughter%20Set%20To%20Become%20First%20Lady%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPakistan%20President%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%20is%20set%20to%20announce%20his%20daughter%2C%20Aseefa%20Bhutto%2C%20as%20the%20First%20Lady%20of%20the%20country%2C%20local%20media%20reports%20claimed.%20If%20this%20happens%2C%20the%20Pakistani%20President%20would%20be%20breaking%20traditions%2C%20as%20normally%20the%20title%20is%20given%20to%20the%20President's%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ECiting%20a%20source%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpresi