igh%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Singh's%20allegation%20was%20that%20when%20journalists%20asked%20Irani%20about%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20the%20petitioner%20against%20her%20personal%20secretary%2C%20Ms%20Irani%20described%20the%20petitioner%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpawn%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20said%20she%20was%20having%20direct%20links%20with%20the%20Gandhi%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuoting%20Irani's%20entire%20conversation%20with%20journalists%2C%20the%20high%20court%20said%20that%20before%20giving%20the%20statement%20in%20question%2C%20Ms%20Irani%20talked%20about%20other%20matters%20and%20during%20this%20time%20she%20did%20not%20even%20take%20the%20name%20of%20the%20petitioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20that%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20petitioner%2C%20Ms%20Irani%20had%20said%20the%20petitioner%20had%20links%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20also%20had%20a%20criminal%20history.%20The%20court%20found%20that%20criminal%20cases%20were%20registered%20against%20the%20petitioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20that%20if%20the%20court%20looks%20at%20Ms%20Irani's%20statements%2C%20she%20was%20criticising%20a%20political%20party%20and%20she%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20defaming%20the%20petitioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710203040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-02%2Fp65uhfbc_smriti-irani-pti-_625x300_08_February_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fallahabad-court-dismisses-shooter-vartika-singhs-plea-against-smriti-irani-5221685%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20has%20dismissed%20international%20shooter%20Vartika%20Singh's%20plea%20challenging%20an%20MP%2FMLA%20court%20order%20rejecting%20her%20defamation%20complaint%20against%20Union%20min