te.com%2Fculture%2F2024%2F03%2Fryan-gosling-oscars-im-just-ken-performance-barbie-slash.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERyan%20Gosling%20to%20sing%20and%20dance%2C%20to%20general%20acclaim%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20%E2%80%A6%20we%20have%20a%20real%20glass%20half-empty%2Fhalf-full%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20per%20ABC%2C%20Sunday%20night's%20show%20drew%2019.5%20million%20viewers%2C%20which%20ABC%20notes%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Ba%204-year%20high%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20third%20year%20in%20a%20row%20that%20the%20audience%20has%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20that's%20good%2C%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%3A%20That%20means%20this%20year's%20telecast%20still%20drew%20considerably%20less%20than%20the%2023.6%20million%20viewers%20who%20watched%20the%202020%20show%2C%20which%20didn't%20have%20anything%20like%20%26quot%3BBarbie%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BOppenheimer%2C%26quot%3B%20box-office-wise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20then%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oscars.org%2Foscars%2Fceremonies%2F2020%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBest%20Picture%3C%2Fa%3E%20nominees%20were%20ones%20regular%20folks%20may%20have%20seen%20in%20theaters%2C%20including%20%26quot%3BFord%20V.%20Ferrari%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BJoker.%26quot%3B%20And%20the%20big%20winner%20that%20night%20was%20%26quot%3BParasite%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Korean-made%20slasher%2Fsatire%2C%20which%20brought%20in%20about%20%24260%20million%20in%20worldwide%20box%20office%20%E2%80%94%20really%20big%20for%20a%20Korean-language%20film%2C%20but%20not%20a%20juggernaut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%3A%20If%20this%20year's%20numbers%2C%20bolstered%20by%20giant%20hits%2C%20are%20a%20win%20for%20the%20Oscars%20%E2%80%A6%20maybe%20we%20have%20to%20accept%20the%20fact%20that%20Oscars%20are%20never%20coming%20anywhere%20close%20to%20all%20the%20way%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20context%3A%20As%20recently%20as%20a%20decade%20ago%