%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20that%20it%20seems%20all%20very%20innocuous%20when%20you're%20flipping%20through%20a%20tabloid%20at%20the%20doctor's%20office%20or%20see%20a%20photo%20of%20a%20pregnant%20lady%20online%2C%20but%20I%20find%20the%20media's%20'bump%20watch'%20obsession%20to%20be%20both%20intrusive%20and%20stressful.%20So%20I%20made%20a%20decision%20to%20eject%20myself%20from%20it%20completely.%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'Annnnd%20I'm%20out.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EApril%202015%3A%20Mendes%20stars%20in%20%26quot%3BLost%20River%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20film%20that%20Gosling%20directed%20and%20co-produced.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22992%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22eva%20%20lost%20river%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5eb040893dac9a018b494c92%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22744%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEva%20Mendes%20starred%20in%20%26quot%3BLost%20River.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EBold%20Films%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMendes%20played%20a%20cabaret%20dancer%20in%20the%202015%20film%20%26quot%3BLost%20River%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20was%20Gosling's%20feature%20film%20directorial%20debut.%20It%20marked%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20couple%20worked%20together%20after%20%26quot%3BThe%20Place%20Beyond%20the%20Pines.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%202019%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oprahmag.com%2Fstyle%2Fa27409832%2Feva-mendes-new-york-and-company-collection-daughters%2F%5C%22%3EOprah%20Magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mendes%20reminisced%20on%20her%20experience%20working%20with%20her%20partner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20two%20times%20we've%20collaborated%2C%20him%20and%20I%2C%20have%20been%20the%20two%20best%20experiences%20in%20my%20career.%20There's%20such%20special%20work%20in%20'The%20Place%20Beyond%20the%20Pines.'%20We%20had%20known%20each%20other%20for%20a%20while%20already%2C%20so%20to%20work%20together%20was%20really%20exci