20relief%20of%20the%20Supreme%2C%20which%20does%20a%20better%20job%20of%20contouring%20to%20your%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Allswell%20Supreme%20has%20three%20layers%20of%20CertiPUR-US%20certified%20foams%20(from%20top%20to%20bottom)%3A%20a%20soft%20Euro%20top%2C%20graphite%20and%20copper%20gel-infused%20memory%20foam%20for%20heat%20dissipation%2C%20and%20pressure-relieving%20foam.%20The%20individually%20wrapped%20coil%20base%20is%20designed%20for%20motion%20isolation%20and%20breathability%20and%20features%20a%20reinforced%20edge%20for%20better%20edge%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mattress%20has%20great%20motion%20isolation%20and%20edge%20support%2C%20suggesting%20it%20would%20be%20optimal%20for%20couples.%20I%20also%20liked%20that%20the%20average%20firmness%20worked%20well%20for%20every%20position%20I%20slept%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Allswell%20Supreme%20Hybrid%20Mattress%20tends%20to%20trap%20heat%2C%20sometimes%20making%20sleeping%20on%20it%20uncomfortable.%20You%20might%20consider%20adding%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-cooling-mattress-topper-for-hot-sleepers%5C%22%3Ecooling%20mattress%20topper%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20you%20tend%20to%20overheat%20like%20me.%20%C2%A0Or%20keep%20it%20as-is%20if%20you%20usually%20get%20cold%20at%20night.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fallswell-supreme-hybrid-mattress-review%5C%22%3EAllswell%20Supreme%20Hybrid%20Mattress%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20luxury%5C%22%3EBest%20luxury%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Saatva%20Classic%20Mattress%20offers%20a%20luxury%20experience%20at%20a%20mid-range%20price.%20It's%20made%20with%20quality%20materials%20and%20comes%20with%20free%20in-home%20set-up%20and%20old%20mattress%20removal.%20Plus%2C%20you%20can%20try%20it%20for%20365%20nights.%20If%20you%20decide%20to%20keep%20it%2C%20it's%20covered%20by%20a%20lifetime%20warranty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20layer%20of%20the%20Classic%20is%20a%203-inch%20Euro%20pillow%20top%20featuring%20an%20organic%20cotton%20cover%20that%20remains%20cool%20to%20the%20touch.%20Below%20is%20a%20layer%20of%20thin%20memory%20foam%20with%20zoned%20support%20where%20you%20need%20it%20most.%20Next%2C%20individually%20wrapped%20pocket%20coils%20contour%20to%20your%20body's%20curves%20to%20offer%20optimal%20spinal%20alignment%20and%20pressure%20relief.%20The%20base%20features%20thicker%20coils%20for%20airflow%20and%20durability.%20The%20mattress%20has%20excellent%20edge%20support%20thanks%20to%20the%20border%20of%20high-density%20foam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tend%20to%20overheat.%20Yet%2C%20while%20testing%20the%20Saatva%20Classic%2C%20I%20stayed%20pretty%20cool.%20It%20comes%20in%20Plush%20Soft%2C%20Luxury%20Firm%2C%20and%20Firm.%20I%20tested%20the%20Luxury%20Firm%2C%20which%20was%20too%20firm%20for%20side%20sleeping.%20Yet%2C%20I%20sank%20in%20just%20enough%20to%20keep%20my%20spine%20neutral%20while%20sleeping%20on%20my%20back.%20The%20Plush%20Soft%20is%20a%20better%20option%20for%20most%20side%20sleepers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESenior%20home%20editor%20Jaclyn%20Turner%2C%20a%20back%20sleeper%2C%20slept%20on%20the%20Saatva%20Classic%20for%20nearly%20two%20years.%20She%20loved%20the%20gentle%20support%20and%20plush%20pillow%20top%2C%20though%20there%20was%20a%20break-in%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Classic%20failed%20our%20bowling%20ball%20test%20and%20had%20higher-than-average%20vibrometer%20readings%2C%20but%20I'd%20say%20the%20motion%20isolation%20is%20average%20based%20on%20my%20subjective%20experience.%20I%20didn't%20feel%20jostled%20when%20pets%20or%20people%20moved%20around%20on%20the%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fsaatva-classic-mattress-review%5C%22%3ESaatva%20Classic%20Mattress%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for