0risk%20to%20smaller%20dogs%2C%20they%20can%20make%20playtime%20more%20frustrating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Kong%20Puppy%20Binkie%20is%20a%20pacifier-shaped%20rubber%20toy%20available%20in%20sizes%20appropriate%20for%20smaller%20muzzles.%20According%20to%20Quest%2C%20soft%20rubber%20toys%20may%20be%20helpful%20for%20soothing%20sore%20gums.%20This%20toy%20also%20has%20an%20opening%20where%20you%20can%20insert%20food%20and%20treats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20large%20breeds%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20buying%20toys%20for%20a%20large%20breed%20puppy%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20they're%20not%20small%20enough%20to%20be%20a%20choking%20risk.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20important%20to%20try%20to%20size%20a%20chew%20toy%20to%20a%20puppy's%20mouth%20size%20so%20they%20can%20comfortably%20fit%20the%20widest%20part%20of%20the%20toy%20between%20their%20upper%20and%20lower%20molars%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Quest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Kong%20Puppy%20Tires%20toy%20comes%20in%20a%20large%20size%20that%20is%204.5%20inches%20in%20diameter.%20Durable%2C%20bouncy%20rubber%20makes%20up%20this%20tire-shaped%20toy%20that%20discourages%20destructive%20chewing.%20The%20inside%20tracks%20of%20the%20tire%20can%20be%20filled%20with%20soft%20food%20to%20hold%20your%20puppy's%20attention%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20bone%3Cp%3EToys%20and%20objects%20made%20of%20very%20hard%20materials%20can%20pose%20a%20tooth%20fracture%20risk%2C%20says%20Quest.%20Instead%20of%20giving%20your%20puppy%20things%20like%20antlers%20or%20real%20bones%2C%20look%20for%20toys%20made%20of%20softer%20materials%20like%20the%20Hurley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bone-shaped%20toy%20is%20made%20from%20a%20stretchy%20yet%20durable%20plastic%20formula%20that%20feels%20more%20like%20rubber.%20The%20toy's%20material%20is%20great%20for%20chewing%20and%20gives%20it%20plenty%20of%20bounce.%20It%20comes%20in%20three%20sizes%2C%20the%20smallest%20being%204.5%20inches%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20multipack%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20'one%20size%20fits%20all'%20product%2C%20as%20each%20puppy%20will%20have%20their%20own%20individual%20chewing%20characteristics%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Quest.%20Some%20puppies%20might%20love%20to%20chew%20on%20solid%20rubber%20toys%2C%20while%20others%20prefer%20textured%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20pack%20of%20three%20different%20textured%20toys%20from%20Outward%20Hound%20combines%20various%20textures%20like%20fabric%20rope%20and%20rubber%20nubs.%20The%20toys%20also%20have%20ridges%20that%20may%20help%20reduce%20tartar%20buildup.%20At%20just%204.75%20inches%20long%20each%2C%20they're%20an%20excellent%20size%20for%20small%20puppy%20jaws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20treat%20dispensing%3Cp%3EPlay%20which%20might%20involve%20chewing%20objects%20or%20other%20puppies%20starts%20at%20about%20three%20weeks%2C%20says%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvcahospitals.com%2Fwest-los-angeles%2Fspecialty%2Fteam%2Fkaren-sueda%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Karen%20Sueda%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20veterinary%20behaviorist%20with%20VCA%20West%20Los%20Angeles%20Animal%20Hospital.%20Puppies%20also%20engage%20in%20more%20exploratory%20behavior%20as%20they%20get%20older%20and%20can%20benefit%20from%20toys%20that%20encourage%20mental%20enrichment%2C%20like%20puzzles%2C%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20take%20advantage%20of%20your%20puppy's%20curiosity%20by%20giving%20them%20enriching%20treat-dispensing%20toys%20like%20the%20Toppl%2C%20our%20top%20pick%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-puppy-toys%5C%22%3Ebest%20puppy%20toys%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20treat%20toy%20has%20a%20hollow%20interior%20where%20you%20can%20insert%20soft%20food%20like%20peanut%20butter%20along%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-puppy-food%5C%22%3Ebest%20puppy%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-treats%5C%22%3Ebest%20dog%20treats%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20dishwasher%20safe%20and%20comes%20in%20two%20sizes%20that%20you%20can%20interlock%20together%20as%20your%20dog%20gets%20older%20%E2%80%94%20and%20smarter!%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20plush%3Cp%3EPetersel%20says%20many%20puppies%20are%20more%20attracted%20to%20soft%2C%20plush-like%20toys%20because%20they%20can%20easily%20sink%20their%20teeth%20into%20them%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they're%20gentle%20on%20the%20teeth%20and%20gums.%20If%20you%20add%20a%20squeaker%20to%20that%2C%20the%20toy%20may%20be%20even%20more%20attractive%20to%20your%20puppy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Invincibles%20Minis%20Dog%20has%20a%20squeaker%20enclosed%20in%20ultra-tough%20fabric%20with%20reinforced%20double-layer%20seams.%20The%20squeaker%20is%20long-lasting%20and%20designed%20to%20keep%20making%20sounds%20even%20if%20punctured.%20Because%20there's%20no%20stuffing%2C%20you'll%20also%20have%20less%20of%20a%20mess%20if%20it%20comes%20apart.%20It's%20appropriate%20for%20small%20and%20medium%20breeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20interactive%3Cp%3EPuzzle%20toys%20provide%20puppies%20with%20a%20physical%20and%20psychological%20challenge%20and%20can%20encourage%20nervous%20dogs%20to%20focus%20their%20attention%20on%20play%2C%20says%20Petersel.%20An%20excellent%20way%20to%20introduce%20your%20dog%20to%20puzzles%20is%20to%20start%20with%20the%20most%20basic%20variation%3A%20the%20Kong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Kong%20is%20a%20good%20choice%20for%20teething%20puppies%20because%20it%20can%20be%20stuffed%20with%20food%2C%20making%20it%20a%20long-lasting%20option%2C%20says%20Petersel.%20It's%20also%20our%20top%20pick%20for%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-toy%5C%22%3Ebest%20dog%20toys%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Whether%20or%20not%20you%20fill%20it%20with%20treats%2C%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20best%20puppy%20teething%20toys%20because%20it's%20made%20of%20flexible%20rubber%20to%20help%20soothe%20teething-related%20gum%20irritation.%20It%20also%20comes%20in%20various%20sizes%20to%20suit%20different%20breeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20ring%3Cp%3EWhile%20regular%20puppy%20play%20usually%20involves%20nipping%20and%20mouthing%20other%20puppies%20in%20the%20same%20litter%2C%20once%20your%20puppy%20is%20part%20of%20your%20household%20%E2%80%94%20and%20possibly%20solo%20%E2%80%94%20they%20may%20start%20using%20their%20mouth%20on%20you%20or%20your%20stuff%2C%20says%20Sueda.%20You%20can%20redirect%20that%20behavior%20onto%20appropriate%20chew%20toys%20like%20the%20SodaPup%20Diamond%20Ring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ring-shaped%20toy's%20nylon%20and%20wood%20composite%20construction%20is%20ideal%20for%20super-chewer%20puppies.%20The%20diamond%20provides%20a%20varied%20shape%20to%20hold%20your%20pup's%20attention%2C%20and%20when%20they%20chew%20on%20it%2C%20it%20may%20help%20keep%20their%20teeth%20clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20ball%3Cp%3EWhile%20balls%20aren't%20necessarily%20the%20best%20option%20for%20long%20chew%20sessions%2C%20Quest%20says%20they're%20appropriate%20for%20interactive%20play%20between%20puppy%20and%20human.%20However%2C%20it's%20essential%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20ball%20is%20not%20small%20enough%20for%20your%20dog%20to%20swallow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dura%20Play%20Ball%20comes%20in%20three%20sizes%20to%20fit%20dogs%20of%20all%20sizes%20and%20ages.%20The%20ball's%20latex%20material%20is%20super%20flexible%20yet%20capable%20of%20handling%20plenty%20of%20gnawing.%20Even%20better%2C%20it%20has%20a%20yummy%20bacon%20scent%20and%20floats%20in%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20fetch%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20important%20thing%20when%20deciding%20what%20kind%20of%20material%20is%20best%20for%20a%20particular%20puppy%20is%20to%20know%20that%20puppy's%20chewing%20style%20and%20habits%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Quest.%20If%20your%20dog%20is%20a%20lighter%20chewer%20and%20doesn't%20tend%20to%20destroy%20toys%2C%20something%20made%20of%20softer%20rubber%2C%20like%20the%20Puppy%20Flyer%20disc%2C%20is%20an%20excellent%20option%20for%20fetch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKong's%20rubber%20formula%20for%20puppies%20is%20suitable%20for%20dogs%20up%20to%209%20months%20old.%20The%20disc%20won't%20hurt%20your%20puppy's%20teeth%20when%20they%20catch%20it%2C%20yet%20it's%20durable%20enough%20for%20playing%20fetch%20outdoors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20puppy%20teething%20toys%3Cp%3EWhen%20shopping%20for%20the%20best%20puppy%20teething%20and%20chew%20toys%2C%20our%20experts%20say%20to%20consider%20your%20puppy's%20age%2C%20size%2C%20and%20chew%20strength%20as%20well%20as%20a%20toy's%20safety%2C%20durability%2C%20and%20materials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAge%20and%20size%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Appropriate%20sizing%20is%20crucial%20when%20choosing%20toys%20for%20any%20dog.%20For%20puppies%2C%20toys%20should%20not%20be%20so%20small%20they%20pose%20a%20choking%20hazard.%20Quest%20says%20it's%20best%20if%20toys%20fit%20comfortably%20between%20your%20dog's%20top%20and%20bottom%20teeth.%20A%20toy%20that's%20too%20big%20might%20not%20do%20much%20to%20soothe%20sore%20gums.%20Once%20your%20dog%20outgrows%20their%20puppy%20toys%2C%20it's%20time%20to%20swap%20them%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EChew%20strength%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Quest%20recommends%20supervising%20your%20puppy%20to%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20how%20they%20interact%20with%20toys.%20Super%20chewers%20might%20need%20more%20durable%20toys%20to%20gnaw%20on%2C%20while%20more%20gentle%20chewers%20might%20prefer%20softer%20toys%20with%20more%20give.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESafety%20and%20durability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Quest%20says%20to%20steer%20clear%20of%20toys%20with%20parts%20that%20your%20pup%20might%20easily%20bite%20off%20and%20swallow.%20It's%20also%20important%20to%20make%20sure%20a%20product%20isn't%20too%20hard.%20%26q