20to%20an%20expert%20who%20would%20analyze%20my%20colors%20for%20me.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221099%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20writer%20next%20to%20a%20checklist%20of%20things%20to%20have%20in%20the%20photo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62fac49ff16a0d0018e6a05d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22819%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20had%20to%20send%20the%20analyst%20photos%20of%20my%20face%20without%20makeup%20in%20natural%20lighting.%3Cp%3EPaige%20DiFiore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20more%20online%20quizzes%20left%20me%20confused%2C%20I%20finally%20caved%20and%20looked%20into%20having%20my%20colors%20analyzed%20by%20a%20pro.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20there%20were%20in-person%20color-analysis%20options%20available%20in%20my%20area%2C%20they%20were%20a%20bit%20out%20of%20my%20budget%2C%20with%20many%20starting%20at%20%24450%20per%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20choosing%20a%20virtual%20color%20analysis%20with%20Dina%20Scherer%2C%20NYC%20wardrobe%20stylist%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.modnitsastyling.com%2F%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.modnitsastyling.com%2F%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1660687467097000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2r6zuOQSfEqkCQZ2zln4VS%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EModnitsa%20Styling%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20cost%20%24130%20and%20came%20with%20a%20virtual%20assessment%2C%2020-minute%20meeting%2C%20and%20a%20personalized%20color%20fan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20meeting%2C%20Dina%20asked%20me%20for%20a%20list%20of%20photos%20that%20she'd%20base%20her%20assessment%20on.%20They%20had%20to%20be%20taken%20in%20natural%20light%20without%20a%20camera%20flash%20or%20makeup.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20I%20needed%20a%20close-up%20photo%20of%20my%20face%2C%20like%20a%20headshot%2C%20and%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20side%20of%20my%20face%20that%20focused%20on%20my%20neck%20and%20ear.%20(Trying%20to%20snap%20a%20close-up%20photo%20of%20my%20side%20profile%20was%20humbling.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20addition%20to%20selfies%2C%20I%20sent%20her%20photos%20of%20my%20palm%20and%20wrist%2C%20which%20would%20help%20her%20determine%20my%20undertone.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221039%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22two%20photos%20of%20the%20authors%20hand%20with%20arrows%20pointing%20to%20wrist%20veins%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62eaa278076fd300189ce31b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22782%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20took%20both%20of%20these%20photos%20in%20front%20of%20the%20same%20window%20and%20I%20still%20don't%20know%20my%20vein%20color.%3Cp%3EPaige%20DiFiore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20picture%20of%20my%20wrist%20and%20the%20palm%20of%20my%20hand%20would%20be%20used%20to%20help%20determine%20my%20undertone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreenish-blue%20veins%20are%20a%20sign%20of%20warm%20undertones%2C%20which%20means%20you%20look%20best%20in%20gold%20jewelry%2C%20according%20to%20Dina.%20She%20said%20blueish-purple%20veins%20are%20a%20sign%20of%20cool%20undertones%2C%20which%20means%20you%20look%20best%20with%20silver%20jewelry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20analyst%20also%20asked%20for%20photos%20of%20me%20wearing%20a%20few%20different%20colors.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20writer%20wearing%20blue%2C%20the%20writer%20wearing%20red%2C%20and%20the%20writer%20wearing%20yellow%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62ea73a9076fd300189cd559%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAgain%2C%20I%20took%20these%20photos%20in%20natural%20lighting%20without%20makeup.%3Cp%3EPaige%20DiFiore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EDina%20wanted%20to%20see%20me%20wearing%20any%20shade%20of%20red%2C%20green%2C%20blue%2C%20orange%2C%20and%20yellow%20to%20%26quot%3Bhelp%20ensure%20the%20most%20accurate%20analysis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EI%20found%20a%20few%20colorful%20tank%20tops%20from%20high%20school%20and%20one%20dark-orange%20cardigan%20that%20I%20wrapped%20around%20myself%20like%20a%20top.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EAfter%20snapping%20these%20photos%2C%20I%20was%20starting%20to%20wonder%20if%20that%20shade%20of%20yellow%20really%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstylists-reveal-mistakes-you-make-when-getting-dressed-every-day-2019-12%5C%22%3Elooked%20as%20good%20on%20me%20as%20I'd%20previously%20thought%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EAfter%20I%20sent%20my%20photos%20in%2C%20Dina%20took%20a%20week%20to%20give%20me%20my%20results.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFinally%2C%20I%20met%20with%20Dina%20to%20get%20my%20results.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221140%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22cool%20vs%20warm%20silver%20and%20gold%20rings%20on%20hand%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62f16084cc15bf00182f75d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22846%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESilver%20is%20best%20on%20people%20with%20cool%20undertones%20and%20gold%20is%20best%20on%20those%20with%20warm%20undertones.%3Cp%3EPaige%20DiFiore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20Dina%20explained%20that%20there%20are%20two%20%26quot%3Bwarm%26quot%3B%20seasons%20(spring%20and%20autumn)%20and%20two%20%26quot%3Bcool%26quot%3B%20seasons%20(winter%20and%20summer).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpring%20and%20autumn%20have%20more%20yellow%20mixed%20into%20their%20ideal%20shades.%20Summers%20and%20winters%20have%20more%20blue%20mixed%20into%20theirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20the%20first%20key%20component%20of%20a%20color%20analysis%20is%20discovering%20your%20undertone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWarm%20undertones%20are%20usually%20represented%20by%20yellow%20gold%20and%20cool%20ones%20by%20silver%20or%20white%20gold.%20Rose%20gold%20is%20often%20in%20the%20middle%2C%20though%20it%20swings%20cool%2C%20Dina%20said.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20put%20it%2C%20%26quot%3Blike%20enhances%20like%26quot%3B%20so%20if%20your%20undertone%20is%20warm%2C%20warm%20colors%20will%20make%20you%20shine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAccording%20to%20Dina%2C%20I%20have%20warm%20undertones.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221144%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20writer%20wearing%20cool%20green%20next%20to%20writer%20wearing%20warm%20green%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62f1873a8677d80018ee6ce5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22857%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOn%20the%20left%2C%20I'm%20wearing%20a%20cool%20blue-green.%20On%20the%20right%2C%20I'm%20wearing%20a%20warmer%20olive%20green.%3Cp%3EPaige%20DiFiore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20dear%20reader%2C%20is%20part%20one%20of%20my%20world%20being%20absolutely%20rocked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20selfies%20I%20sent%2C%20Dina%20said%20I%20have%20warm%20undertones.%20She%20said%20she%20was%20most%20clearly%20able%20to%20determine%20my%20undertone%20by%20seeing%20how%20I%20looked%20wearing%20different%20colors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20orange%20looked%20great%20on%20me%2C%20she%20said%2C%20but%20the%20green%20shirt%20(left)%20wasn't%20quite%20right%20because%20it%20was%20cool-toned.%20A%20warm-toned%20green%20(right)%20would%20make%20me%20look%20better.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBecause%20I'm%20warm-toned%2C%20she%20said%2C%20gold%20jewelry%20would%20flatter%20me%20much%20more%20than%20silver.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221091%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22writer%20with%20silver%20and%20gold%20necklaces%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62f161b3cc15bf00182f763a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22818%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGold%20is