0%E2%80%94%20the%20lightness%20and%20darkness%20between%20your%20eyes%2C%20skin%2C%20and%20hair.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EContrast%2C%20she%20explained%2C%20is%20something%20people%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ecan%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Echange%20with%20things%20like%20makeup%2C%20hair%20dye%2C%20or%20colored%20contacts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20hazel%20eyes%20match%20my%20dark%20brown%20hair%20pretty%20closely%2C%20but%20my%20skin%20is%20fair.%20Those%20factors%20make%20me%20medium-to-high%20contrast%2C%20according%20to%20my%20color%20pro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20my%20eyes%20were%20icy%20blue%2C%20I%20could%20be%20higher%20contrast.%20If%20my%20skin%20was%20darker%2C%20I%20could%20be%20lower%20contrast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20key%20component%20of%20this%20analysis%20came%20down%20to%20softness%20versus%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDina%20said%20softness%20looks%20more%20at%20similarities%2C%20like%20brown%20hair%20and%20hazel%20eyes.%20Clarity%20looks%20more%20at%20a%20stark%2C%20defined%20contrast%20%E2%80%94%20like%20black%20hair%20and%20blue%20eyes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20my%20hair%20color%20is%20similar%20to%20my%20eye%20color%2C%20Dina%20said%2C%20I%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20softness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAt%20last%2C%20Dina%20narrowed%20me%20down%20to%20the%20two%20warm%20seasons.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221195%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tessa%20thompson%2C%20taylor%20swift%2C%20victoria%20pedreddi%2C%20ana%20de%20armas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F630554b3c2794d00197f4386%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22599%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETessa%20Thompson%20and%20Taylor%20Swift%20are%20springs.%20Victoria%20Pedretti%20and%20Ana%20de%20Armas%20are%20autumns.%3Cp%3EJon%20Kopaloff%2FGetty%20Images%3B%20Kevin%20Mazur%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Netfilx%3B%20Amanda%20Edwards%2FWireImage%20via%20Getty%20Images%3B%20HENRY%20NICHOLLS%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20to%20my%20surprise%2C%20my%20final%20judgment%20came%20down%20to%20the%20warm%20seasons%20%E2%80%94%20spring%20and%20autumn%2C%20a%20season%20I%20initially%20dismissed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20seasons%20are%20considered%20warm%20by%20color%20experts%2C%20but%20autumns%20look%20best%20in%20soft%2C%20refined%20colors%2C%20and%20springs%20shine%20in%20bright%2C%20energetic%20ones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Jackson's%20book%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20differences%20between%20autumns%20and%20springs%20are%20that%20many%20springs%20tend%20to%20flush%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAccording%20to%20Dina%2C%20I%20am%20a%20%26quot%3Btrue%20autumn.%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221144%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20writer%20in%20a%20warm%20orange%20color%20and%20the%20writer%20in%20a%20cool%20brown%20color%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62f16349cc15bf00182f767c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22856%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20warm%20brown%20definitely%20makes%20me%20pop%20more%20than%20the%20cool%20one%20does.%3Cp%3EPaige%20DiFiore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERemember%20when%20I%20said%20I%20didn't%20think%20beige%2C%20gold%2C%20and%20orange%20were%20my%20colors%3F%20Apparently%2C%20I%20was%20very%2C%20very%20wrong.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDina%20said%20my%20best%20neutrals%20%E2%80%94%20colors%20that%20pair%20well%20with%20others%20%E2%80%94%20are%20brown%2C%20off-white%2C%20and%20olive%20green.%20She%20said%20I%20should%20avoid%20stark%20white%20and%20black%2C%20two%20colors%20that%20only%20shine%20on%20winters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20some%20of%20my%20power%20colors%20%E2%80%94%20ones%20that%20flatter%20me%20the%20most%20and%20should%20be%20sprinkled%20throughout%20my%20wardrobe%20%E2%80%94%20are%20olive%20green%2C%20violet%2C%20orange%2C%20and%20navy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20what%20Dina%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Btrue%20autumn%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20the%20brightest%20version%20of%20autumn%20colors%20will%20often%20look%20best%20on%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20these%20colors%20apply%20to%20makeup%2C%20which%20got%20me%20thinking%20about%20how%20I%20already%20love%20wearing%20orange%20and%20gold%20eye%20shadow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20undertone%20was%20a%20deciding%20factor%20in%20my%20season.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221144%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Navy%20shirt%20vs%20black%20shirt%2C%20writer%20wearing%20both%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62f172a4cc15bf00182f7af6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22857%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENavy%20(left)%20is%20my%20power%20color%20but%20black%20(right)%20is%20not.%3Cp%3EPaige%20DiFiore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESomething%20Dina%20really%20emphasized%20is%20that%20if%20you%20love%20a%20color%20that's%20not%20%26quot%3Bin%20your%20season%26quot%3B%20you%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-know-if-your-clothes-dont-actually-fit%5C%22%3Estill%20find%20a%20way%20to%20rock%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20instead%20of%20emerald%20green%20(winter)%20I%20should%20try%20olive%20green%20(autumn).%20Instead%20of%20sapphire%20(winter)%20or%20black%20(winter)%2C%20I%20should%20try%20navy%20(autumn).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20difference%20can%20seem%20subtle%20and%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20it%20was%20a%20placebo%20effect%2C%20but%20my%20skeptical%20self%20was%20starting%20to%20board%20the%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20an%20autumn%26quot%3B%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20noticing%20a%20difference%20in%20my%20face%20when%20I%20wore%20a%20power%20color%20or%20one%20of%20my%20not-so-flattering%20ones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDina%20also%20explained%20why%20I'm%20not%20a%20winter%20like%20I'd%20initially%20suspected.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221194%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22julia%20roberts%2C%20the%20writer%2C%20liv%20tyler.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C