rs%20to%20moving%20more%20of%20the%20computation%20closer%20to%20the%20user%20(the%20%26quot%3Bedge%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20network).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20it's%20your%20smartphone%2C%20an%20autonomous%20car%2C%20or%20a%20security%20device%20in%20your%20home%2C%20edge%20computing%20means%20more%20of%20the%20heavy%20lifting%20happens%20on%20or%20near%20the%20device.%20That%20change%20could%20lead%20to%20lower%20latency%2C%20lower%20energy%20costs%2C%20and%20improved%20privacy%20and%20security%20as%20less%20sensitive%20information%20gets%20beamed%20to%20some%20far-flung%20server.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20behind%20edge%20computing%20is%20nothing%20new%2C%20but%20the%20AI%20gold%20rush%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5g-advanced-standalone-6g-qualcomm-huawei-mwc-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimprovements%20to%205G%3C%2Fa%3E%20make%20it%20a%20perfect%20time%20for%20the%20space%20to%20take%20off.%205G%20lets%20devices%20on%20the%20edge%20communicate%20with%20one%20another%20and%20the%20cloud.%20While%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5g-advanced-standalone-6g-qualcomm-huawei-mwc-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E5G%20had%20a%20slow%20and%20messy%20start%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20recent%20advancements%20could%20prove%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20edge%20computing%2C%20which%20will%20require%20data%20connections%20to%20run%20seamlessly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20had%20eyed%20edge%20computing%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-web-services-internal-memo-edge-computing-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20billion-dollar%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%20The%20buzz%20around%20AI%20and%20its%20potential%20for%20edge%20computing%20also%20ignited%20talk%20at%20the%20Mobile%20World%20Congress%2C%20held%20in%20Barcelona%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJim%20Poole%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20global%20business%20development%20at%20Equinix%2C%20said%20at%20an%20MWC%20panel%20that%20the%20move%20toward%20edge%20computing%20is%20accelerating%20in%20part%20because%20of%20the%20AI%20boom%2C%20which%20requires%20much%20more%20data%20to%20be%20processed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BData%20gravity%20is%20a%20real%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Poole%20said.%20%26quot%3BAt%20some%20point%2C%20it%20becomes%20financially%20and%20physically%20impossible%20to%20transmit%20that%20data%20all%20the%20way%20back%20to%20someplace%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latency%20benefits%20of%20edge%20are%20crucial%20with%20technologies%20such%20as%20driverless%20cars%2C%20which%20need%20to%20make%20split-second%20decisions.%20That's%20why%20autonomous%20vehicles%20have%20powerful%20computers%20that%20live%20on%20the%20vehicle%20itself.%20The%20same%20goes%20for%20medical%20equipment%20or%20devices%20used%20in%20dangerous%20types%20of%20manufacturing%2C%20where%20more%20computing%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20on%20the%20fly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Qualcomm%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5dc454fc3afd3715334f8226%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20China%20International%20Import%20Expo%20in%20Shanghai.%3Cp%3EAly%20Song%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EAI%20accelerates%20edge%20computing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20industry%20has%20already%20seen%20some%20benefits%20of%20edge%20in%20smartphones%2C%20with%20a%20push%20to%20create%20better%20chips%20and%20software%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-smartphones-mwc-artificial-intelligence-assistants-apps-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20allow%20more%20AI%20horsepower%20onto%20devices%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20will%20also%20require%20AI%20companies%20to%20launch%20smaller%20language%20models%20that%20can%20run%20on%20less%20powerful%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Taiwanese%20chip%20company%20MediaTek%20had%20one%20of%20the%20most%20impressive%20demos%20at%20MWC%20this%20year%3A%20a%20smartphone-like%20device%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffranticnews%2Fstatus%2F1762453559302398321%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erunning%20a%20generative%20image%20maker%3C%2Fa%3E%20powered%20by%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstability-ai-ceo-employees-going-die-openai-google-meta-report-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStable%20Diffusion%3C%2Fa%3E%20AI%20model%2C%20which%20created%20and%20edited%20pictures%20in%20real%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELenovo%2C%20which%20was%20also%20at%20the%20show%2C%20is%20making%20a%20big%20enterprise%20play%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgadget.co.za%2Flenovoai2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eselling%20its%20%26quot%3Bedge%20AI%26quot%3B%20servers%20to%20businesses%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20has%20plans%20to%20make%20moves%20in%20edge%20for%20consumers%2C%20Tom%20Butler%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20Lenovo's%20laptop%20line%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20think%20of%20bringing%20in%20generative%20workloads%20to%20device%2C%20first%20of%20all%2C%20I%20solve%20for%20time%2C%20security%2C%20and%20privacy%2C%20because%20I'm%20not%20pushing%20up%20to%20cloud%20and%20back%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEdge%20computing%20could%20save%20energy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShifting%20AI%20closer%20to%20the%20user%20could%20have%20cost%20benefits%20for%20tech%20companies%20like%20OpenAI%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20Amazon%2C%20which%20run%20AI%20models%20on%20their%20servers%20at%20great%20expense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEdge%20computing%20could%20also%20have%20environmental%20benefits.%20The%20data%20centers%20that%20power%20AI%20in%20the%20cloud%20use%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-water-use-soaring-ai-make-it-worse-data-centers-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenormous%20amount%20of%20water%20and%20energy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJillian%20Kaplan%2C%20the%20head%20of%20global%205G%20at%20Dell%2C%20said%20during%20an%20MWC%20panel%20that%20edge%20computing%20will%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20energy%20saver.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%20I%20think%20the%20sustainability%20topic%20has%20come%20and%20gone%20throughout%20the%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaplan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20it's%20going%20to%20fluctuate%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%2C%20where%20we%20are%2C%20it%20has%20to%20stay%20top%20of%20mind%2C%20and%20these%20edge%20and%20AI%20capabilities%20are%20going%20to%20help%20us%20keep%20our%20equipment%20extremely%20energy%20efficient%2C%20which%20we%20have%20to%20do%20with%20the%20massive%20amounts%20of%20data%20coming%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-edge-computing-5g-cloud-artificial-intelligence-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710189698000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ef1e9090413ab8e1db5c00%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-edge-computing-5g-cloud-artificial-intelligence-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20edge-computing%20boom%20could%20reduce%20costs%20and%20the%20environmental%20impact%20of%20powering%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20just%20getting%20started.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hlangley%40insider.com%20(Hugh%20Langley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-edge-computing-5g-cloud-artificial-intelligence-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rec