end%20peaked%20at%201%2C691%20wallets%20on%20March%201.%20Given%20the%20decentralized%20nature%20of%20crypto%2C%20it's%20difficult%20to%20determine%20the%20ownership%20details%20behind%20these%20addresses%2C%20and%20it%20is%20possible%20that%20multiple%20wallets%20belong%20to%20a%20single%20person%20or%20entity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20beginning%20of%20this%20month%2C%20bitcoin%20has%20gained%20another%2016%25%2C%20extending%20a%20bull%20run%20that%20first%20kicked%20off%20in%20mid-January%2C%20when%20regulators%20approved%20spot%20bitcoin%20ETFs%20to%20begin%20trading%20in%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBitcoin's%20new-found%20success%20may%20be%20indicative%20that%20the%20cryptocurrency%20is%20here%20to%20stay%20as%20a%20mainstream%20investment%2C%20Rockefeller%20International%20Chair%20Ruchir%20Sharma%20wrote%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F4d869e6a-a974-45fe-b204-cb5f85838352%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20token's%202022%20peak-and-crash%20may%20have%20validated%20crypto-skeptics%2C%20its%20rapid%20rebound%20underlines%20a%20more%20solid%20investment%20thesis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBack%20in%202021%2C%20bitcoin%20was%20often%20grouped%20alongside%20other%20favorites%20of%20the%20day-trading%20crowd%2C%20such%20as%20unprofitable%20tech%20and%20meme%20stocks.%20Today%20those%20other%20bubblets%20are%20trading%20on%20average%20at%20half%20their%20peaks%2C%20while%20bitcoin%20recently%20hit%20an%20all-time%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharma%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20extremely%20unusual%20for%20a%20bubble%20to%20burst%20and%20then%20recover%20to%20reach%20new%20heights%20so%20quickly%2C%20and%20suggests%20that%20something%20real%20and%20sustainable%20is%20going%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESharma%20noted%20that%20around%2070%25%20of%20bitcoin%20accounts%20are%20dormant%2C%20meaning%20that%20investors%20are%20