20which%20unsuccessfully%20sought%20extension%20of%20time%20till%20June%2030%20to%20disclose%20the%20details%20of%20electoral%20bonds.%20The%20court%20asked%20senior%20advocate%20Harish%20Salve%2C%20who%20was%20representing%20the%20bank%2C%20about%20the%20steps%20taken%20by%20the%20SBI%20to%20comply%20with%20its%20landmark%20February%2015%20order%20that%20scrapped%20the%20scheme%20of%20anonymous%20political%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Salve%2C%20our%20judgement%20is%20dated%20February%2015%2C%202024.%20We%20are%20now%20on%20the%2011th%20of%20March.%20In%20the%20last%2026%20days%2C%20what%20extent%20of%20matching%20has%20been%20done%20by%20you%3F%20What%20steps%20have%20you%20taken%20in%20the%20last%2026%20days%3F%20The%20application%20is%20absolutely%20silent%20on%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%20earlier%20directed%20the%20SBI%2C%20the%20authorised%20financial%20institution%20under%20the%20scheme%2C%20to%20submit%20the%20details%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20purchased%20since%20April%2012%2C%202019%20till%20date%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20by%20March%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SBI%2C%20however%2C%20filed%20an%20application%20before%20the%20court%20two%20days%20before%20the%20expiry%20of%20the%20deadline%20seeking%20an%20extension%20of%20time%20until%20June%2030%20for%20complying%20with%20the%20directions.%20In%20its%20application%2C%20the%20SBI%20had%20contended%20that%20the%20retrieval%20of%20information%20from%20%26quot%3Beach%20silo%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20procedure%20of%20matching%20the%20information%20of%20one%20silo%20to%20that%20of%20the%20other%20would%20be%20a%20time-consuming%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Salve%20said%20if%20the%20matching%20exercise%20was%20to%20be%20done%20away%20with%2C%20the%20SBI%20could%20complete%20the%20exercise%20within%20three%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20not%20told%20you%20to%20do%20the%20matching%20exercise.%20We%20have%20asked%20you%20for%20a%20plain%20disclosure%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20your%20FAQs%20(frequently%20asked%20question)%2C%20which%20were%20shown%20to%20us%20during%20the%20hearing%2C%20indicate%20that%20for%20every%20purchase%2C%20you%20have%20to%20have%20a%20separate%20KYC%20(know%20your%20customer)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20noting%2C%20%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20it%20is%20very%20clear%20that%20every%20time%20somebody%20made%20a%20purchase%2C%20a%20KYC%20was%20mandated%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20put%20the%20SBI%20on%20notice%20that%20it%20may%20be%20inclined%20to%20proceed%20against%20it%20for%20%26quot%3Bwilful%20disobedience%26quot%3B%20of%20its%20February%2015%20verdict%20if%20the%20bank%20failed%20to%20comply%20with%20its%20directions%20and%20timelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710185760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-05%2F51qsbfd_election-commission-reuters_625x300_05_May_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-asked-by-supreme-court-to-publish-electoral-bonds-data-by-march-15-5220405%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Election%20Commission%20is%20likely%20to%20make%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20data%20public%20on%20its%20website%20soon%20after%20the%20expected%20disclosure%20by%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-asked-by-supreme-court-to-publish-electoral-bonds-data-by-march-15-5220405%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-asked-by-supreme-court-to-publish-electoral-bonds-data-by-march-15-5220405%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-asked-by-supreme-court-to-publish-