2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-election%2Fsc-rejects-sbi-plea-bank-to-give-electoral-bond-details-to-eci-on-mar-12-124031101109_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-election%2Fsc-rejects-sbi-plea-bank-to-give-electoral-bond-details-to-eci-on-mar-12-124031101109_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BKey%20Issues%26quot%3B%20That%20Citizenship%20Law%20CAA%20May%20Solve%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20implemented%20the%20contentious%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20or%20CAA%20on%20Monday%2C%20four%20years%20after%20the%20controversial%20law%20was%20passed.%20The%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%202019%2C%20seeks%20to%20grant%20Indian%20citizenship%20to%20refugees%20who%20had%20sought%20shelter%20in%20India%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014%2C%20due%20to%20religious%20persecution%20in%20three%20neighbouring%20countries%20--%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20has%20now%20spelt%20out%20the%20%26quot%3Bkey%20issues%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20implementation%20of%20CAA%20might%20be%20able%20to%20solve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%20would%20help%20to%20remove%20%26quot%3Blegal%20barriers%20to%20rehabilitation%20and%20citizenship%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bgive%20a%20dignified%20life%20to%20refugees%20who%20have%20suffered%20for%20decades%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20government%20sources%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20asserted%20that%20citizenship%20rights%20will%20protect%20the%20cultural%2C%20linguistic%2C%20and%20social%20identity%20of%20the%20refugees%20while%20ensuring%20economic%2C%20commercial%2C%20free%20movement%2C%20and%20property%20purchase%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20sharp%20criticism%20from%20the%20opposition%20rank%2C%20the%20Centre%20categorically%20said%20that%20CAA%20%26quot%3Bwill%20not%20take%20away%20citizenship%20of%20any%20Indian%20citizen%2C%20irrespective%20of%20religion%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20Act%20is%20only%20for%20those%20who%20have%20suffered%20persecution%20for%20years%20and%20have%20no%20other%20shelter%20in%20the%20world%20except%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20other%20Opposition%20parties%20have%20slammed%20the%20move%2C%20alleging%20the%20new%20law%20that%20was%20implemented%20just%20days%20before%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20election%20schedule%20was%20designed%20to%20polarise%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20especially%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Constitution%20of%20India%20grants%20the%20government%20the%20right%20to%20provide%20citizenship%20from%20a%20humanitarian%20perspective%20to%20refugees%20who%20faced%20religious%20persecution%20in%20their%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20also%20clarified%20that%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20was%20delayed%20due%20to%20the%20Covid%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%202019%20manifesto%2C%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20said%20it%20was%20committed%20to%20enacting%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Bill%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20persecuted%20religious%20minorities%20from%20neighbouring%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710183840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Ftoub2pl8_caa-registration_625x300_11_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act-government-on-key-issues-that-citizenship-law-caa-may-solve-5220716%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Government%20implemented%20the%20contentious%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20or%20CAA%20on%20Monday%2C%20four%20years%20after%20the%20controversial%20law%20was%20passed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act-government-on-key-issues-that-citizenship-la