%3EThe%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20on%20Monday%20refused%20to%20grant%20an%20interim%20stay%20on%20setting%20up%20a%20fact-checking%20unit%20(FCU)%20under%20the%20recently%20amended%20Information%20Technology%20(IT)%20Rules%20to%20identify%20fake%20and%20false%20content%20on%20social%20media%20against%20the%20government%2C%20noting%20that%20no%20grave%20and%20irreparable%20loss%20would%20be%20caused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20single%20bench%20of%20Justice%20A%20S%20Chandurkar%20said%20no%20case%20was%20made%20out%20to%20direct%20the%20government%20to%20continue%20its%20earlier%20statement%20that%20it%20would%20not%20notify%20the%20FCU%20pending%20hearing%20of%20petitions%20against%20the%20IT%20Rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20was%20passed%20on%20a%20bunch%20of%20applications%20filed%20by%20standup%20comedian%20Kunal%20Kamra%20and%20others%20seeking%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20notification%20of%20the%20FCU%20pending%20the%20final%20disposal%20of%20their%20pleas%20against%20the%20IT%20Rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20the%20balance%20of%20convenience%20tilts%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20government%20as%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20has%20made%20a%20categorical%20submission%20that%20political%20opinions%2C%20satire%20and%20comedy%20are%20aspects%20not%20sought%20to%20be%20linked%20to%20the%20business%20of%20the%20Central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotifying%20the%20FCU%20would%20not%20result%20in%20an%20irreversible%20situation%20as%20any%20action%20taken%20post%20the%20notification%20would%20always%20be%20subject%20to%20the%20final%20orders%20of%20this%20court%20on%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20IT%20Rules%2C%20the%20high%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20situation%2C%20when%20pitted%20against%20the%20larger%20public%20interest%2C%20leads%20me%20to%20opine%20that%20grave%20and%20irreparable%20loss%20is%20not%20shown%20to%20result%20if%20the%20FCU%20is%20notified%2C%20warranting%20the%20passing%20of%20an%20interim%20direction%20of%20not%20notifying%20the%20FCU%20till%20the%20challenge%20to%20the%20Rules%20is%20finally%20decided%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Chandurkar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20noted%20that%20the%20petitioners%20apprehend%20that%20that%20exchange%20of%20information%20in%20the%20form%20of%20political%20discourses%20or%20comments%2C%20political%20satire%2C%20and%20so%20on%20may%20be%20targeted%20if%20the%20FCU%20is%20notified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Solicitor%20General%20has%20said%20the%20FCU%20intends%20only%20to%20deal%20with%20government%20business%20in%20its%20strict%20sense%2C%20and%20it%20did%20not%20aim%20or%20attempt%20to%20prevent%20or%20muzzle%20political%20views%2C%20satire%2C%20sarcasm%20or%20political%20comments%2C%20it%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20this%20prima%20facie%20stage%2C%20in%20my%20view%2C%20the%20stand%20taken%20by%20the%20non-applicant%20(Centre)%20allays%20the%20apprehension%20expressed%20by%20the%20applicants%20that%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20'Central%20Government%20business'%2C%20the%20FCU%20would%20prevent%20expression%20of%20political%20views%20or%20comments%2C%20sarcasm%2C%20political%20satire%20or%20dissent%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Chandurkar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pleas%20against%20the%20IT%20Rules%20were%20referred%20to%20Justice%20Chandurkar%20after%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Gautam%20Patel%20and%20Neela%20Gokhale%20delivered%20a%20split%20verdict%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Justice%20Patel%20struck%20down%20the%20impugned%20Rules%2C%20terming%20them%20unconstitutional%2C%20Justice%20Gokhale%20upheld%20them%20and%20dismissed%20the%20petitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Patel%20had%20said%20the%20Rules%20amount%20to%20censorship%2C%20but%20Justice%20Gokhale%20had%20opined%20they%20do%20not%20have%20any%20chilling%20effect%20on%20free%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20division%20bench%20had%20also%20differed%20on%20whether%20a%20stay%20should%20be%20granted%20on%20setting%20up%20the%20FCU%20pending%20a%20hearing%20on%20the%20pleas%20by%20the%20third%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Patel%20had%20said%20the%20FCU%20should%20not%20be%20notified%2C%20and%20Justice%20Gokhale%20opined%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Chandurkar%20on%20Monday%20said%20the%20interim%20applications%20would%20now%20be%20placed%20before%20the%20referral%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Patel%20and%20Gokhale%20for%20orders%20on%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Justice%20Chandurkar's%20opinion%2C%20the%20Centre%20would%20get%20clearance%20to%20notify%20the%20FCU%20under%20the%20IT%20Rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20Centre%20gave%20an%20oral%20assurance%20to%20the%20court%20that%20it%20would%20not%20notify%20the%20FCU%20under%20the%20IT%20Rules%20until%20the%20final%20verdict%20was%20delivered%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20the%20division%20bench's%20split%20verdict%2C%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20submitted%20to%20the%20court%20that%20the%20oral%20assurance%20could%20be%20extended%20only%20until%20the%20third%20judge%20took%20up%20the%20matter%20for%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20then%20filed%20interim%20applications%20seeking%20a%20stay%20on%20notification%20of%20the%20FCU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%206%2C%202023%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20promulgated%20certain%20amendments%20to%20the%20Information%20Technology%20(Intermediary%20Guidelines%20and%20Digital%20Media%20Ethics%20Code)%20Rules%2C%202021%2C%20including%20a%20provision%20for%20an%20FCU%20to%20flag%20fake%2C%20false%20or%20misleading%20online%20content%20related%20to%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20IT%20Rules%2C%20if%20the%20FCU%20comes%20across%20or%20is%20informed%20about%20any%20posts%20that%20are%20fake%2C%20false%2C%20and%20contain%20misleading%20facts%20about%20the%20business%20of%20the%20government%2C%20it%20would%20flag%20off%20the%20same%20to%20social%20media%20intermediaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20such%20a%20post%20is%20flagged%20off%2C%20the%20intermediary%20has%20the%20option%20of%20either%20taking%20down%20the%20post%20or%20putting%20a%20disclaimer%20on%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20taking%20the%20second%20option%2C%20the%20intermediary%20loses%20its%20safe%20harbour%2Fimmunity%20and%20stands%20liable%20for%20legal%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710182940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2F85mh9qus_bombay-high-court-website-photo_625x300_20_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-interim-stay-on-fact-checking-unit-under-it-rules-bombay-high-court-5220717%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20on%20Monday%20refused%20to%20grant%20an%20interim%20stay%20on%20setting%20up%20a%20fact-checking%20unit%20(FCU)%20under%20the%20recently%20amended%20Information%20Technology%20(IT)%20Rules%20to%20identify%20fake%20and%20false%20content%20on%20social%20media%20against%20the%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-interim-stay-on-fact-checking-unit-under-it-rules-bombay-high-court-5220717%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-interim-stay-on-fact-checking-unit-under-it-rules-bombay-high-court-5220717%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-interim-stay-on-fact-checking-unit-under-it-rules-bombay-high-court-5220717%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Yodha%20has%20got%20my%20best%20of%20action%20sequences%3A%20Sid%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710182883000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22http