y%2C%20Anakapalle%2C%20Tirupati%2C%20Narasapuram%20and%20one%20more%20seat%20while%20Jana%20sena%20from%20Machilipatnam%20and%20Kakinada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20came%20after%20senior%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20including%20Union%20Minister%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%2C%20went%20into%20a%20huddle%20with%20Mr%20Naidu%20and%20Mr%20Kalyan%20on%20Monday%20to%20finalise%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%20announced%20the%20alliance%20of%20his%20party%20with%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20and%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20on%20March%209.%20%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20dynamic%20and%20visionary%20leadership%20of%20Hon'ble%20Prime%20Minister%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%20Ji%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20and%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20Party%20(JSP)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20being%20committed%20to%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20country%20and%20the%20upliftment%20of%20state%20and%20people%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20have%20decided%20to%20contest%20the%20ensuing%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20elections%20together%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20joint%20statement%20released%20by%20the%20TDP%20BJP%20and%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TDP%2C%20which%20was%20part%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20until%202018%2C%20expressed%20interest%20in%20reviving%20the%20alliance%20after%20suffering%20a%20crushing%20defeat%20in%20the%202019%20elections.%20Mr%20Naidu's%20party%20had%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20NDA%20over%20financial%20support%20for%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20%26quot%3BI%20took%20the%20decision%20not%20for%20selfish%20reasons%20but%20for%20the%20interests%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20For%20four%20years%20I%20made%20all%20efforts%2C%20went%20to%20Delhi%2029%20times%2C%20asked%20many%20times.%20This%20was%20the%20Centre's%20last%20budget%20and%20there%20was%20no%20mention%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Naidu%20had%20then%20explained%20his%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20joint%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20parties%20highlighted%20their%20%26quot%3Bold%20ties%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20and%20the%20TDP%20have%20a%20very%20old%20relationship%20together.%20The%20TDP%20joined%20the%20NDA%20in%201996%20and%20has%20worked%20together%20successfully%20in%20governments%20led%20by%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20the%20TDP%20and%20the%20BJP%20fought%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20polls%20together%2C%20while%20the%20JSP%20supported%20the%20two%20parties%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20said%20that%20he%20was%20ready%20to%20fight%20against%20the%20alliance%20and%20alleged%20that%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20cycle%20is%20%26quot%3Brusted%20and%20he%20is%20fetching%20support%20from%20other%20political%20parties%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElections%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20held%20in%20April-May%20in%20which%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20is%20eyeing%20a%20third%20term%20and%20has%20set%20a%20target%20of%20winning%20370%20seats%20on%20its%20own%20and%20400%20with%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710181920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F3pfgv0u8_chandrababu-naidu-ani-_625x300_08_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-chandrababu-naidus-tdp-and-pawan-kalyans-jana-sena-finalise-seats-for-lok-sabha-andhra-polls-5220446%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BJP%2C%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20TDP%20and%20Pawan%20Kalyan's%20Jana%20Sena%20finalise%20seats%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Andhra%20polls%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-chandrababu-naidus-tdp-and-pawan-kalyans-jana-sena-finalise-seats-for-lok-sabha-andhra-polls-5220446%22