3EMr%20Azad%2C%20though%2C%20was%20coy.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20ruling%20out%20contesting%20from%20Anantnag-Rajouri%20parliament%20constituency%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2075-year-old%20who%20has%20also%20served%20as%20a%20Union%20Minister%20in%20the%20UPA%20government%20led%20by%20Manmohan%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLots%20of%20people%20are%20asking%20me%20to%20contest.%20Demand%20of%20my%20being%20in%20the%20parliament%20is%20more...%20but%20there%20are%20voices%20who%20want%20me%20contest%20assembly%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Mr%20Azad's%20entry%2C%20Anantnag%20could%20see%20a%20four%20cornered%20contest.%20The%20seat%20was%20once%20considered%20a%20stronghold%20of%20the%20PDP%2C%20though%20National%20Conference%20won%20it%20in%20the%20last%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Mufti%2C%20is%20tipped%20to%20be%20contesting%20from%20Anantnag%20seat.%20In%20last%20parliament%20election%20she%20came%20number%20three%20and%20pointing%20to%20her%20party's%20poor%20performance%2C%20Omar%20Abdullah%20has%20refused%20to%20concede%20the%20seat%20to%20PDP%20even%20though%20both%20parties%20are%20part%20of%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20state%20unit%20chief%20Ravinder%20Raina%20is%20also%20extensively%20campaigning%20in%20the%20area%2C%20holding%20rallies%20in%20what%20literally%20were%20no-go%20areas%20for%20the%20BJP%20till%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Mr%20Azad%20--%20who%20for%20long%20has%20been%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20--%20this%20would%20be%20his%20first%20test%20of%20popularity%20in%20his%20home%20state%20after%20his%20exit%20from%20the%20Congress.%20It%20would%20also%20make%20Anantnag%20an%20avidly%20watched%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Azad's%20Lok%20Sabha%20stint%20was%20in%20the%201980s%20from%20Maharashtra's%20Washim%20constituency%2C%201991%20onwards%2C%20he%20has%20been%20a%20member%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20In%202014%2C%20he%20contested%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Udhampur%20and%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Azad%20has%20launched%20his%20own%20party%20Democratic%20Progressive%20Azad%20Party%20or%20DPAP%20after%20his%20exit%20from%20the%20Congress%20and%20has%20been%20making%20scathing%20attacks%20on%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20functioning%20of%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20member%20of%20the%20committee%20on%20%26quot%3BOne%20Nation%20One%20election%26quot%3B%20headed%20by%20former%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%2C%20Mr%20Azad%20said%20he%20strongly%20supports%20simultaneous%20polls%20for%20parliament%20and%20J%26amp%3BK%20assembly%2C%20which%20are%20long%20overdue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20is%20visiting%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20to%20review%20the%20preparedness%20for%20elections.%20There%20are%20reports%20that%20the%20Commission%20is%20considering%20simultaneous%20elections%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20in%20favor%20of%20simultaneous%20elections%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20The%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20are%20more%20concerned%20about%20assembly%20elections%20than%20parliament%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20elected%20government%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20collapsed%20in%20June%202018%20as%20the%20BJP%20withdrew%20from%20the%20alliance%20with%20Ms%20Mufti's%20PDP.%C2%A0%20In%202019%2C%20the%20state%20was%20bifurcated%20into%20two%20Union%20Territories%20and%20its%20special%20status%20under%20the%20Constitution%20was%20scrapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20has%20since%20been%20under%20President's%20Rule.%20The%20BJP%20calls%20it%20an%20improvement%20on%20the%20governments%20led%20by%20local%20parties.%20%26quot%3BToday%20poor%20people%20are%20getting%20their%20rights.%20PM%20Modi%20has%20given%20golden%20(health%20card)%20to%20every%20resident%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ravinder%20Raina.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Azad%20said%20after%20his%20exit%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20he%20held%20around%20600%20public%20meetings%20across%20J%26amp%3BK%20over%20the%20last%2018%20months.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20very%20satisfied%20that%20I%20have%20formed%20my%20own%20party.%20There%20is%20overwhelming%20response%20from%20all%20sections%20of%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20But%20his%20real%20challenge%20will%20be%20to%20convert%20this%20enthusiasm%20into%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710177180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F2hoo62b4_ghulam-nabi-azad-ani_625x300_24_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fghulam-nabi-azad-may-contest-from-kashmir-first-popularity-test-after-quitting-congress-5220056%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Veteran%20political%20leader%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%2C%20who%20quit%20Congress%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20is%20ready%20to%20join%20the%20electoral%20fray%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fghulam-nabi-azad-may-contest-from-kashmir-first-popularity-test-after-quitting-congress-5220056%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fghulam-nabi-azad-may-contest-from-kashmir-first-popularity-test-after-quitting-congress-5220056%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fghulam-nabi-azad-may-contest-from-kashmir-first-popularity-test-after-quitting-congress-5220056%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aditya%20Birla%20Finance%20may%20merge%20with%20Aditya%20Birla%20Cap%20within%20next%2012%20months%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710176973000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-08%2F27%2Ffull%2F1630083883-7009.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.c