nt%2C%20and%20property%20purchase%20rights%20for%20these%20migrants%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fgovt-notifies-rules-for-implementation-of-caa-ahead-of-election-dates-124031101159_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fgovt-notifies-rules-for-implementation-of-caa-ahead-of-election-dates-124031101159_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fgovt-notifies-rules-for-implementation-of-caa-ahead-of-election-dates-124031101159_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPM%20Modi%20Has%20Delivered%20On%20Another%20Commitment%26quot%3B%3A%20Amit%20Shah%20On%20CAA%20Rules%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20on%20Monday%20implemented%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%202019%2C%20notifying%20the%20rules%20four%20years%20after%20the%20contentious%20law%20was%20passed%20by%20Parliament%20to%20fast-track%20citizenship%20for%20undocumented%20non-Muslim%20migrants%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Afghanistan%20who%20came%20to%20India%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20unveiling%20of%20the%20rules%20that%20came%20days%20ahead%20of%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20will%20now%20start%20granting%20Indian%20nationality%20to%20persecuted%20non-Muslim%20migrants%20--%20Hindus%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Jains%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Parsis%20and%20Christians%20--%20from%20the%20three%20countries.%20The%20rules%20come%20into%20force%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Gazette%20notification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20delivered%20on%20another%20commitment%20and%20realised%20the%20promise%20of%20the%20makers%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficial%20sources%20said%20CAA-2019%20is%20a%20law%20to%20give%20citizenship%20and%20will%20not%20take%20away%20citizenship%20of%20any%20Indian%20irrespective%20of%20their%20religion%2C%20adding%20it%20is%20only%20for%20those%20who%20have%20suffered%20persecution%20for%20years%20and%20have%20no%20other%20shelter%20in%20the%20world%20except%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20misconceptions%20have%20been%20spread%20regarding%20the%20CAA%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%20secured%20Parliament's%20approval%20in%20December%202019%20and%20subsequently%20got%20the%20President's%20assent%20but%20there%20were%20protests%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20against%20it%2C%20with%20many%20opposition%20parties%20speaking%20out%20against%20the%20law%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bdiscriminatory%26quot%3B.%20Over%20100%20people%20lost%20their%20lives%20during%20the%20anti-CAA%20protests%20or%20police%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20rules%20will%20now%20enable%20minorities%20persecuted%20on%20religious%20grounds%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Afghanistan%20to%20acquire%20citizenship%20in%20our%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20this%20notification%2C%20PM%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%20Ji%20has%20delivered%20on%20another%20commitment%20and%20realised%20the%20promise%20of%20the%20makers%20of%20our%20Constitution%20to%20the%20Hindus%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Jains%2C%20Parsis%20and%20Christians%20living%20in%20those%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20Minister%20Shah%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20Modi%20government%20today%20notified%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Rules%2C%202024.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThese%20rules%20will%20now%20enable%20minorities%20persecuted%20on%20religious%20grounds%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Afghanistan%20to%20acquire%20citizenship%20in%20our%20nation.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWith%20this%20notification%20PM%20Shri%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40narendramodi%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ji%20has%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Amit%20Shah%20(Modi%20Ka%20Parivar)%20(%40AmitShah)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAmitShah%2Fstatus%2F1767192979197104180%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Home%20Ministry%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20applications%20will%20be%20submitted%20in%20a%20completely%20online%20mode%20for%20which%20a%20web%20portal%20has%20been%20provided.%20The%20law%20could%20not%20come%20into%20effect%20as%20rules%20had%20not%20been%20notified%20till%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20opposition%20parties%20slammed%20the%20government's%20step%2C%20alleging%20the%20new%20law%20is%20designed%20to%20polarise%20the%20coming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20especially%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Assam%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20called%20it%20historic%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bhumanitarian%20decision%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20general%20secretary%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20alleged%20that%20the%20announcement%20is%20yet%20another%20attempt%20to%20%26quot%3Bmanage%20the%20headlines%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20strictures%20on%20Monday%20on%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20seeking%20nine%20extensions%20for%20the%20notification%20of%20the%20rules%2C%20the%20timing%20right%20before%20the%20elections%20is%20evidently%20designed%20to%20polarise%20the%20elections%2C%20especially%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Assam%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20Chief%20Minister%20Pinaray%20Vijayan%20described%20the%20CAA%20as%20a%20communally%20divisive%20law%20and%20asserted%20that%20it%20will%20not%20be%20implemented%20in%20the%20southern%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20alleged%20that%20the%20Centre's%20move%20is%20against%20the%20country%20and%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bdirty%20politics%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20BJP%20to%20make%20poor%20people%20from%20neighbouring%20countries%20its%20vote%20bank%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20said%20she%20would%20fiercely%20oppose%20the%20CAA%20if%20she%20found%20it%20to%20be%20discriminatory%20against%20groups%20of%20people%20living%20in%20India%20and%20if%20it%20curtailed%20their%20existing%20citizenship%20rights%20in%20any%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%20supremo%20was%20talking%20to%20reporters%20just%20minutes%20before%20the%20CAA%20rules%20were%20officially%20notified%20by%20the%20Centre%2C%20West%20Bengal's%20Matua%20community%20celebrated%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20citizenship%20law%20at%20the%20headquarters%20of%20the%20sect%20at%20Thakurnagar%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%2C%20claiming%20it%20to%20be%20their%20%26quot%3Bsecond%20independence%20day%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatuas%2C%20originally%20from%20East%20Pakistan%2C%20are%20a%20weaker%20section%20of%20Hindus%20who%20migrated%20to%20India%20during%20the%20Partition%20and%20after%20the%20creation%20of%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20community%2C%20with%20an%20estimated%20population%20of%20three%20million%20in%20the%20state%2C%20can%20tilt%20the%20scales%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20political%20party%20in%20more%20than%2030%20assembly%20seats%20in%20Nadia%2C%20and%20North%20and%20South%2024%20Parganas%20districts%20bordering%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistani%20Hindu%20refugees%2C%20who%20have%20been%20living%20a%20life%20of%20uncertainty%2C%20welcomed%20the%20government's%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20refugees%20residing%20in%20Delhi%20said%20they%20were%20elated%20and%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Bwill%20finally%20be%20called%20Indian%20citizens%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECelebrations%20also%20erupted%20in%20the%20Majnu%20ka%20Tilla%20area%20where%20they%20mostly%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20All%20Assam%20Students'%20Union%20(AASU)%20and%2030%20indigenous%20organisations%20burnt%20copies%20of%20the%20CAA%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20Assam%2C%20including%20Guwahati%2C%20Barpeta%2C%20Lakhimpur%2C%20Nalbari%2C%20Dibrugarh%20and%20Tezpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2016-party%20United%20Opposition%20Forum%2C%20Assam%2C%20(UOFA)%20announced%20a%20statewide%20hartal%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20besides%20taking%20up%20other%20agitational%20programmes%20in%20a%20phased%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20continue%20with%20our%20non-violent%2C%20peaceful%2C%20democratic%20movement%20against%20CAA.%20Alongside%2C%20we%20will%20also%20continue%20our%20legal%20fight%2C%26quot%3B%20AASU%20advisor%20Samujjal%20Bhattacharjya%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhattacharjya%20asserted%20that%20the%20indigenous%20people%20of%20Assam%20and%20North-East%20will%20never%20accept%20CAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Manual%20on%20Parliamentary%20Work%2C%20the%20rules%20for%20any%20legislation%20should%20be%20framed%20within%20six%20months%20of%20presidential%20assent%20or%20the%20government%20has%20to%20seek%20an%20extension%20from%20the%20Committees%20on%20Subordinate%20Legislation%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202020%2C%20the%20Home%20Ministry%20has%20been%20taking%20extensions%20at%20regular%20intervals%20from%20the%20parliamentary%20committee%20for%20framing%20the%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20document%20will%20be%20sought%20from%20the%20applicants%2C%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20was%20stepped%20up%20in%20Shaheen%20Bagh%2C%20Jamia%20Nagar%20and%20other%20areas%20of%20the%20national%20capital%20as%20well%20as%20in%20various%20states%20which%20had%20earlier%20witnessed%20anti-CAA%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20notified%20rules%2C%20the%20Applicants%20for%20Indian%20citizenship%20will%20have%20to%20continuously%20spend%20at%20least%2012%20months%20in%20India%20preceding%20the%20date%20of%20the%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rules%20also%20said%20that%20during%20the%20eight%20years%20immediately%20preceding%20the%20said%20period%20of%20twelve%20months%2C%20the%20applicants%20will%20have%20to%20spend%20at%20least%20a%20total%20of%20six%20years%20in%20India%20to%20be%20eligible%20to%20get%20Indian%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20applicants%20will%20also%20have%20to%20give%20a%20declaration%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Birrevocably%26quot%3B%20renounce%20the%20existing%20citizenship%20and%20that%20they%20want%20to%20make%20%26quot%3BIndia%20a%20permanent%20home%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20will%20have%20to%20declare%20that%20they%20will%20not%20lay%20claim%20on%20the%20renounced%20citizenship%20in%20future%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20cleared%20applicants%20will%20have%20to%20take%20an%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20affirming%20that%20they%20will%20%26quot%3Bbear%20true%20faith%20and%20allegiance%20to%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%26quot%3B%20as%20by%20law%20established%20and%20that%20they%20would%20%26quot%3Bfaithfully%20observe%20the%20laws%20of%20India%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bfulfil%26quot%3B%20their%20duties%20as%20a%20citizen%20of%20India%2C%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710176220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fqm726cno_amit-shah-ani_625x300_02_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-has-delivered-on-another-commitment-amit-shah-on-caa-rules-5220142%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Centre%20on%20Monday%20implemented%20the%20Citizenship%2