ore-money-through-distribution-reveals-film-historian-dilip-thakur%2Farticleshow%2F108405266.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Telangana%2C%20BRS%20Suffers%20Another%20Setback%20as%20BJP%20Engineers%20Defections%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11202507%2FDefectors-II.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EHyderabad%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20BJP%20has%20kept%20a%20hawkish%20eye%20on%20leaders%20from%20the%20main%20opposition%20party%20in%20Telangana%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samiti%20(BRS)%20%E2%80%93%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20poach%20them%20into%20contesting%20on%20its%20behalf%20in%20the%20upcoming%20parliamentary%20elections%20from%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20announced%20a%20ticket%20to%20B.B.%20Patil%2C%20the%20sitting%20BRS%20MP%20from%20Zaheerabad%2C%20overnight%20after%20the%20BRS%20had%20confirmed%20his%20candidature%20from%20the%20same%20constituency.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20soon%20as%20he%20resigned%20from%20the%20primary%20membership%20of%20the%20BRS%2C%20the%20BJP%20rolled%20out%20the%20red%20carpet%20for%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20same%20way%2C%20the%20BJP%20announced%20the%20candidature%20of%20Bharat%20Prasad%20from%20the%20Nagarkurnool%20(SC%20reserved)%20constituency%20within%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20of%20his%20father%20and%20sitting%20MP%20from%20the%20constituency%20P.%20Ramulu%20tendering%20his%20resignation%20from%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERamulu%20was%20keen%20on%20handing%20over%20the%20mantle%20to%20his%20son.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20two%20former%20MPs%20of%20the%20BRS%2C%20Ajmeera%20Sitaram%20Naik%20(Mahbubabad)%20and%20Godam%20Nagesh%20(Adilabad)%2C%20and%20two%20former%20MLAs%2C%20Jalagam%20Venkat%20Rao%20(Kothagudem)%20and%20S.%20Saidi%20Reddy%20(Huzurnagar)%2C%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EG.%20Srinivas%2C%20a%20BRS%20candidate%20who%20unsuccessfully%20contested%20the%20parliamentary%20elections%20from%20Peddapalli%20in%202009%2C%20also%20joined%20the%20BJP%20on%20the%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20of%20them%20were%20likely%20to%20get%20tickets%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20defections%20by%20BRS%20leaders%20had%20rattled%20its%20leadership%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20party%20was%20having%20a%20tough%20time%20finding%20strong%20candidates%20to%20contest%20the%20coming%20elections%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20its%20defeat%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%20three%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22In%20Telangana%2C%20Five%20Trends%20Highlight%20Divides%2C%20Gains%2C%20Losses%20and%20Blows%20to%20Expansion%20Plans%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-bharat-rashtra-samithi-congress-kcr%5C%22%3EIn%20Telangana%2C%20Five%20Trends%20Highlight%20Divides%2C%20Gains%2C%20Losses%20and%20Blows%20to%20Expansion%20Plans%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESenior%20leaders%20like%20former%20minister%20T.%20Harish%20Rao%20swung%20into%20action%20and%20contacted%20former%20BRS%20MLA%20Aroori%20Ramesh%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20convince%20him%20after%20he%20threatened%20to%20walk%20out%20and%20contest%20from%20Warangal%20(SC%20reserved)%20on%20a%20BJP%20ticket.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERao%20also%20called%20up%20half%20a%20dozen%20corporators%20of%20the%20Warangal%20municipal%20corporation%20to%20stop%20them%20from%20switching%20over%20to%20the%20Congress%20when%20they%20had%20declared%20their%20intentions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20a%20lower%20level%2C%20the%20BRS%20leaders%20who%20had%20no%20stakes%20in%20the%20elections%20went%20with%20the%20wind%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20engineered%20the%20defections%2C%20mainly%20targeting%20BRS%20leaders%20who%20are%20potential%20election%20material.%20The%20party%20has%20four%20MPs%20and%20hopes%20to%20add%20two%20more%20to%20the%20tally%20realistically%2C%20though%20on%20record%2C%20its%20leaders%20claimed%20they%20targeted%20winning%20ten%20out%20of%2017%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBJP%20state%20secretary%20S.%20Prakash%20Reddy%20said%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20immediate%20goal%20was%20to%20overtake%20the%20BRS%20in%20terms%20of%20numbers%20to%20take%20the%20second%20spot%20behind%20the%20ruling%20Congress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20will%20stand%20the%20BJP%20in%20good%20stead%20to%20assume%20power%20in%20the%202028%20assembly%20elections%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20idea%20was%20to%20erase%20the%20BRS%20from%20the%20political%20spectrum%20by%202028.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESenior%20BRS%20leader%20and%20former%20chairman%20of%20the%20state%20planning%20board%20B.%20Vinod%20Kumar%20admitted%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20trying%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdevour%E2%80%9D%20the%20BRS.%20He%20said%20the%20BJP%20was%20playing%20the%20snake-and-ladder%20game%20but%20warned%20that%20the%20BRS%20will%20climb%20up%20the%20ladder%20again%20if%20it%20went%20down.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVinod%20Kumar%20said%20that%20half%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20candidates%2C%20including%20its%20well%20known%20faces%20like%20former%20minister%20Eatala%20Rajender%2C%20were%20from%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20won%20eight%20assembly%20seats%20recently%2C%20up%20from%20just%20one%20in%20the%202018%20polls%2C%20and%20also%20improved%20its%20vote%20share%20from%207%25%20to%2014%25%20during%20the%20five-year%20period.%20The%20party%20aims%20to%20consolidate%20on%20these%20gains%20with%20an%20improved%20performance%20in%20the%20coming%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-bjp-brs-and-the-truth-behind-the-conspiracy-theories%5C%22%3ETelangana%2C%20BJP%2C%20BRS%20and%20the%20Truth%20Behind%20the%20Conspiracy%20Theories%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20B.B.%20Patil%20and%20Bharat%20Prasad%2C%20others%20whose%20candidature%20was%20announced%20previously%20are%20Union%20tourism%20minister%20G.%20Kishan%20Reddy%20(Secunderabad)%2C%20D.%20Arvind%20(Nizamabad)%20and%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20(Karimnagar)%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20are%20sitting%20MPs%3B%20as%20well%20as%20Madhavi%20Latha%20(Hyderabad)%2C%20Konda%20Vishweshwar%20Reddy%20(Chevella)%2C%20Boora%20Narsaiah%20Goud%20(Bhongir)%20and%20Eatala%20Rajender%20(Malkajgiri).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20the%20latest%20entrants%2C%20ex-MPs%20Sitaram%20Naik%20and%20Godam%20Nagesh%20were%20tipped%20to%20retain%20their%20constituencies%2C%20Mahbubabad%20and%20Adilabad%20respectively.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20Jalagam%20Venkat%20Rao%20expected%20a%20ticket%20from%20Khammam%2C%20Saidi%20Reddy%20from%20Nalgonda%20and%20G.%20Srinivas%20from%20Peddapalli.%20That%20leaves%20decision-making%20to%20be%20completed%20for%20Warangal%2C%20Medak%20and%20Mahbubnagar%2C%20where%20there%20is%20stiff%20competition%20for%20selection%20between%20former%20minister%20D.K.%20Aruna%20and%20ex-MP%20A.P.%20Jitender%20Reddy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20BJP%20discard%20and%20noted%20educationist%20Malka%20Komaraiah%20has%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20BRS%20as%20a%20potential%20contestant%20from%20Malkajgiri%2C%20where%20the%20former%20party%20has%20fielded%20Eatala%20Rajender.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BRS%20has%20so%20far%20announced%20only%20five%20candidates%20amidst%20the%20spate%20of%20desertions%20and%20unwillingness%20of%20some%20of%20its%20leaders%20to%20enter%20the%20poll%20fray.%20Among%20the%20latter%20are%20the%20sitting%20MP%20of%20Chevella%20G.%20Ranjeet%20Reddy%20and%20strongman%20C.%20Malla%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20son%20Bhadra%20Reddy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20had%20recently%20pulled%20down%20a%20college%20building%20and%20road%20infrastructure%20constructed%20by%20Malla%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20son-in-law%20and%20MLA%2C%20Rajasekhar%20Reddy%2C%20for%20various%20permissions%20violations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOtherwise%2C%20Malla%20Reddy%2C%20a%20former%20minister%20who%20runs%20a%20chain%20of%20professional%20colleges%20as%20well%20as%20a%20huge%20health%20city%2C%20made%20a%20strong%20pitch%20for%20his%20son%20Bhadra%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20candidature%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20BRS%20from%20Malkajgiri.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11203737%2FMalha-Reddy-1024x461.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11203737%2FMalha-Reddy-1024x461.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11203737%2FMalha-Reddy-300x135.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11203737%2FMalha-Reddy.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701168%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22378%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMalla%20Reddy%20is%20a%20two-time%20Telangana%20MLA%20and%20was%20also%20MP%20from%20its%20Malkajgiri%20seat.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40chmallareddyMLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20demolition%2C%20Malla%20Reddy%20rushed%20to%20the%20government%20with%20a%20request%20to%20join%20the%20Congress.%20He%20assured%20Congress%20leaders%20that%20he%20would%20mobilise%20a%20crowd%20of%20one%20lakh%20for%20his%20joining%20ceremony.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20sitting%20MP%20P.%20Ramulu%20quit%20the%20BRS%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%20as%20his%20request%20for%20the%20elevation%20of%20his%20son%20Bharat%20Prasad%20as%20chairman%20of%20the%20Nagarkurnool%20zilla%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eparishad%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20turned%20down%20by%20BRS%20president%20and%20former%20Telangana%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekar%20Rao.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERamulu%20and%20Patil%E2%80%99s%20resignations%20from%20the%20BRS%20had%20a%20deep%20impact%20on%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20prospects%20as%20the%20two%20constituencies%20were%20considered%20strong%20bets%20for%20it%20in%20the%20parliamentary%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20accommodated%20Bharat%20Prasad%20in%20Nagarkurnool%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20Shruti%2C%20daughter%20of%20former%20party%20president%20Bangaru%20Laxman%2C%20who%20was%20its%20candidate%20in%20the%20last%20election.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20election%20from%20Nagarkurnool%20has%20assumed%20significance%20this%20time%20following%20an%20alliance%20between%20the%20BRS%20and%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP).%20The%20BRS%20has%20conceded%20the%20seat%20to%20BSP%20state%20president%20and%20former%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20officer%20R.S.%20Praveen%20Kumar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20leaving%20the%20seat%20to%20the%20BSP%20and%20announcing%20candidates%20in%20five%20other%20constituencies%2C%20the%20BRS%20is%20waiting%20for%20rival%20parties%20to%20release%20their%20lists%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20discards%20coming%20its%20way%20to%20join%20the%20battle%20lines.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BRS%20candidates%20so%20far%20are%20B.%20Vinod%20Kumar%20(Karimnagar)%3B%20sitting%20MPs%20Nama%20Nageswara%C2%A0%20Rao%20(Khammam)%2C%20M.%20Kavitha%20(Mahbubabad)%20and%20M.%20Srinivas%20Reddy%20(Mahbubnagar)%3B%20and%20former%20minister%20Koppula%20Easwar%20(Peddapalli).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20sitting%20MP%2C%20N.%20Venkatesh%20(Peddapalli)%2C%20joined%20the%20Congress%20earlier%20but%20has%20not%20figured%20in%20the%20first%20list%20of%20four%20candidates%20released%20by%20the%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChandrashekar%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20daughter%2C%20Kavitha%2C%20who%20had%20lost%20the%20previous%20election%20from%20Nizamabad%2C%20is%20a%20doubtful%20starter%20as%20the%20family%20had%20reportedly%20decided%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20fielding%20her%20this%20time%20around.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710173730000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11202507%2FDefectors-II.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-telangana-brs-suffers-another-setback-as-bjp-engineers-defections%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Having%20improved%20its%20vote%20share%20from%207%25%20to%2014%25%20between%20the%202018%20and%202023%20assembly%20elections%2C%20Telangana's%20BJP%20aims%20to%20consolidate%20on%20these%20gains%20with%20an%20improved%20performance%20in%20the%20general%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-telangana-brs-suffers-another-setback-as-bjp-engineers-defections%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Five%20Skiers%20Found%20Dead%2C%20One%20Missing%20In%20Swiss%20Alps%20Tragedy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20tragic%20accident%20unfolded%20in%20the%20Swiss%20Alps.%20On%20Sunday%2C%20search%20parties%20recovered%20the%20bodies%20of%20five%20missing%20skiers.%20The%20search%20for%20a%20sixth%20person%20continues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C