atna%20home%2C%20Modi%20called%20Yadav%2C%20purportedly%20to%20inquire%20about%20his%20health%20which%20a%20section%20of%20the%20media%20interpreted%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfeeler%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20prime%20minister.%20The%20ailing%20RJD%20chief%20vehemently%20scotched%20such%20reports%2C%20roaring%20in%20no%20uncertain%20terms%2C%20%E2%80%9CNever%E2%80%A6never%20shall%20I%20compromise%20with%20the%20communal%20forces%2C%20whatever%20the%20situation%20is.%20I%20am%20here%20to%20fight%20the%20fascist%20forces%2C%20my%20fight%20will%20continue%E2%80%A6%3Cem%3Eraaj%20rahe%20ya%20jai%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(in%20power%20or%20out%20of%20power%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20he%20was%20convicted%20in%20back%20to%20back%20cases%20of%20the%20fodder%20scam%20and%20was%20jailed%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20treated%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20special%20CBI%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FPolitics%2FFvANkiDXeaFl7bmsOUX8qN%2FThe-secret-of-Lalu-Prasad-Yadavs-survival-in-the-face-of-co.html%5C%22%3Econvicted%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20October%202013.%20He%20was%20an%20MP%20from%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Saran%20seat%20at%20that%20time.%20He%20lost%20his%20membership%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20was%20barred%20from%20contesting%20the%20polls.%20The%20then%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government%20brought%20out%20an%20ordinance%2C%20giving%20three%20months%20reprieve%20to%20the%20convicted%20law-makers%20to%20retain%20their%20seats%20that%20would%20have%20allowed%20Yadav%20to%20contest%20the%202014%20elections.%20But%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Frahul-gandhi-trashes-ordinance-shames-government%2Farticleshow%2F23180950.cms%5C%22%3Etore%20up%20that%20ordinance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20embarrassing%20his%20own%20government%20and%20hurting%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20getting%20the%20biggest%20ever%20blow%20in%20his%20political%20career%20from%20none%20other%20than%20an%20ally%2C%20Yadav%20didn%E2%80%99t%20speak%20a%20word%20either%20against%20Gandhi%20or%20against%20the%20Congress%20and%20stayed%20steadfast%20in%20his%20tirade%20against%20the%20%3Cem%3ESangh%20parivar%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftejashwi-yadav-jan-vishwas-rally-modi-nitish%5C%22%3EPM%E2%80%99s%20Factory%20of%20Lies%2C%20Jobs%20and%20His%20%E2%80%98Uncle%E2%80%99%3A%20What%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20Spoke%20of%20in%20His%20Patna%20Rally%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight%20from%20the%20beginning%20of%20his%20political%20career%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20who%20rose%20to%20power%20as%20a%20crusader%20against%20corruption%20was%20opposed%20to%20Yadav.%20He%20shied%20away%20from%20sharing%20dais%20with%20Yadav%20and%20was%20wary%20of%20shaking%20hands%20with%20the%20latter%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20guard%20his%20%E2%80%9Chonest%20image%E2%80%9D.%20Now%2C%20two%20of%20Kejriwal%E2%80%99s%20colleagues%2C%20Satendra%20Jain%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh%20are%20in%20jail%20and%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20has%20issued%20eight%20summon%20notices%20to%20him%20in%20corruption%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20keeping%20all%20these%20things%20behind%2C%20Yadav%20was%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJj3QFMqycog%5C%22%3E%20seen%20giving%20tips%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Gandhi%20in%20preparing%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Edesi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20mutton%20at%20his%20daughter%2C%20Misa%20Bharti%E2%80%99s%20home%20at%20New%20Delhi%20recently.%20Insiders%20revealed%20that%20Yadav%20was%20very%20warm%20to%20Kejriwal%20too%20during%20INDIA%20bloc%20conclaves%20at%20Patna%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Gandhi%20and%20Kejriwal%20must%20have%20changed%20their%20perception%20about%20Yadav.%20Af