ct.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68536266.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68536266.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Joins%20Elite%20List%20With%20Mission%20Divyastra%3A%20Nations%20That%20Have%20MIRV%20Tech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20joined%20the%20select%20group%20of%20nations%20with%20Multiple%20Independently%20Targetable%20Re-entry%20Vehicle%20or%20MIRV%20technology%20with%20the%20first%20flight%20test%20of%20Mission%20Divyastra.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20congratulated%20the%20scientists%20of%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20for%20the%20first%20flight%20test%20of%20a%20made-in-India%20Agni-5%20missile%2C%20capable%20of%20deploying%20multiple%20warheads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProud%20of%20our%20DRDO%20scientists%20for%20Mission%20Divyastra%2C%20the%20first%20flight%20test%20of%20indigenously%20developed%20Agni-5%20missile%20with%20Multiple%20Independently%20Targetable%20Re-entry%20Vehicle%20(MIRV)%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20posted%20on%20'X'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EProud%20of%20our%20DRDO%20scientists%20for%20Mission%20Divyastra%2C%20the%20first%20flight%20test%20of%20indigenously%20developed%20Agni-5%20missile%20with%20Multiple%20Independently%20Targetable%20Re-entry%20Vehicle%20(MIRV)%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1767159762108465538%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20director%20is%20a%20woman%20and%20it%20has%20a%20significant%20contribution%20from%20women%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%20The%20weapon%20system%20is%20equipped%20with%20indigenous%20avionics%20systems%20and%20high-accuracy%20sensor%20packages%20which%20ensured%20that%20the%20re-entry%20vehicles%20reached%20the%20target%20points%20within%20the%20desired%20accuracy%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Are%20MIRVs%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20Independently-targetable%20Reentry%20Vehicles%20permit%20a%20missile%20to%20deploy%20multiple%20nuclear%20warheads%20to%20different%20targets%20in%20contrast%20to%20a%20traditional%20missile%20that%20carries%20one%20warhead.%20The%20warheads%20on%20these%20missiles%20can%20be%20released%20at%20different%20speeds%20and%20directions.%20Some%20MIRVed%20missiles%20can%20hit%20targets%20as%20far%20as%201%2C500%20kilometres%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20developed%20in%20the%20early%201960s%2C%20MIRV%20technology%20requires%20the%20combination%20of%20large%20missiles%2C%20small%20warheads%2C%20accurate%20guidance%2C%20and%20a%20complex%20mechanism%20for%20releasing%20warheads%20sequentially%20during%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MIRVed%20missiles%20that%20are%20land-based%20are%20considered%20destabilising%20because%20these%20are%20much%20more%20significant%20targets%20than%20traditional%20missiles%20as%20several%20warheads%20can%20be%20taken%20out%20at%20once%20by%20an%20attacker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECountries%20With%20MIRV%20Technology%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20was%20the%20first%20country%20to%20develop%20this%20technology.%20It%20deployed%20a%20MIRVed%20Intercontinental%20Ballistic%20Missile%20(ICBM)%20in%201970%20and%20a%20MIRVed%20Submarine-Launched%20Ballistic%20Missile%20(SLBM)%20in%201971.%20The%20Soviet%20Union%20followed%20suit%20and%20developed%20their%20MIRV-enabled%20ICBM%20and%20SLBM%20technology%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%201970s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20the%20US%2C%20UK%20and%20France%20have%20MIRVed%20SLBMs%2C%20China%20has%20MIRVed%20ICBMs%20while%20Russia%20uses%20both%20MIRVed%20ICBMs%20and%20SLBMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20reports%2C%20Pakistan%20is%20also%20experimenting%20with%20MIRV%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710170640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fgl6ummdg_agni5-mirv-test-_625x300_11_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-joins-elite-list-with-mission-divyastra-agni-5-with-multiple-independently-targetable-re-entry-vehicle-nations-that-have-mirv-tech-5219018%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20joined%20the%20select%20group%20of%20nations%20with%20Multiple%20Independently%20Targetable%20Re-entry%20Vehicle%20or%20MIRV%20technology%20with%20the%20first%20flight%20test%20of%20Mission%20Divyastra.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-joins-elite-list-with-mission-divyastra-agni-5-with-multiple-independently-targetable-re-entry-vehicle-nations-that-have-mirv-tech-5219018%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-joins-elite-list-with-mission-divyastra-agni-5-with-multiple-independently-targetable-re-entry-vehicle-nations-that-have-mirv-tech-5219018%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-joins-elite-list-with-mission-divyastra-agni-5-with-multiple-independently-targetable-re-entry-vehicle-nations-that-have-mirv-tech-5219018%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20to%20develop%20non-personal%20data%20collection%20platform%20for%20India%20Inc%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710170534000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-03%2F11%2Ffull%2F1710169486-1253.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fcentre-to-develop-non-personal-data-collection-platform-for-india-inc-124031101007_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Govt%20plans%20to%20develop%20foundational%20models%20with%20a%20capacity%20of%20m