993_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fhealth%2Fastrazeneca-mankind-pharma-partner-for-distribution-of-asthma-medication-124031100993_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDesigned%20To%20Polarise%20Elections%26quot%3B%3A%20Opposition%20Attacks%20Centre%20Over%20CAA%20Move%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20on%20Monday%20attacked%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20over%20the%20timing%20of%20its%20decision%20to%20notify%20the%20controversial%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20(CAA)%20rules%2C%20saying%20the%20notification%20move%20near%20the%20date%20of%20announcement%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20dates%20is%20%26quot%3Bevidently%20designed%20to%20polarise%20the%20elections%2C%20especially%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Assam%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20seeks%20to%20provide%20citizenship%20to%20Hindus%2C%20Jains%2C%20Christians%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Buddhists%20and%20Parsis%20who%20came%20to%20India%20on%20or%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20taken%20four%20years%20and%20three%20months%20for%20the%20Modi%20Government%20to%20notify%20the%20rules%20for%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20that%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20Parliament%20in%20December%202019%2C%26quot%3B%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20seeking%20nine%20extensions%20for%20the%20notification%20of%20the%20rules%2C%20the%20timing%20right%20before%20the%20elections%20is%20evidently%20designed%20to%20polarise%20the%20elections%2C%20especially%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Assam%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20with%20CAA%20implementation%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20delivered%20on%20another%20commitment%20and%20realised%20promise%20of%20makers%20of%20our%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata