citizens%20gave%20up%20their%20citizenship%20of%20the%20country%20during%20their%2010%20years%20of%20rule.%20No%20matter%20what%20happens%20tomorrow%20you%20have%20to%20give%20account%20of%20'Electoral%20Bond'%20and%20then%20also%20of%20the%20'care%20fund'%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710168780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-08%2Findia-crowd-generic-istock_650x400_61503730268.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdesigned-to-polarise-elections-opposition-attacks-centre-over-caa-move-5219459%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20on%20Monday%20attacked%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20over%20the%20timing%20of%20its%20decision%20to%20notify%20the%20controversial%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20(CAA)%20rules.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdesigned-to-polarise-elections-opposition-attacks-centre-over-caa-move-5219459%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdesigned-to-polarise-elections-opposition-attacks-centre-over-caa-move-5219459%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdesigned-to-polarise-elections-opposition-attacks-centre-over-caa-move-5219459%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Salman%20posts%20birthday%20note%20for%20Saajan%20Singh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710168534000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108402033%2Cimgsize-28544.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsalman-khan-posts-birthday-note-for-choreographer-saajan-singh-latter-reacts-with-gratitude%2Farticleshow%2F108402052.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofin