20a%20lost%20decade!%20All%20the%20promises%20were%20jumlas%20%E2%80%A6%20empty%20promises!%20Power%20now%20rests%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20two%20or%20three%20leaders%2C%20who%20are%20less%20and%20less%20accountable%20to%20the%20voters%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20declaration%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20press%20release%2C%20the%20declaration%20was%20earlier%20adopted%20and%20released%20on%20February%2021%20at%20the%20Kittur%20Fort%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20about%2050%20kilometres%20from%20Belagavi%20in%20Karnataka%20%E2%80%94%20as%20part%20of%20an%20event%20commemorating%20200%20years%20of%20Kittur%20Rani%20Chennamma%E2%80%99s%20revolt%20against%20the%20British%20Empire.As%20per%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(previously%20called%20Twitter)%20by%20social%20activist%20Shabnam%20Hashmi%2C%202500%20women%20participated%20in%20the%20event%20at%20Kittur%20Fort%20%E2%80%9Cto%20expose%20the%20misdeeds%20of%20the%20present%20regime%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOver%202500%20women%20release%20The%20Kittur%20Declaration%20pledging%20to%20expose%20the%20misdeeds%20of%20the%20present%20regime%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20and%20declare%20halla%20bol%20on%20the%20anti%20people%20%2C%20authoritarian%20fascist%20govt%20.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FH7biCXUClP%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FH7biCXUClP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Shabnam%20Hashmi%20(%40ShabnamHashmi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FShabnamHashmi%2Fstatus%2F1760220759929081996%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2021%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20declaration%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20time%20for%20us%20women%20to%20speak%20up%20and%20reclaim%20our%20land%2C%20livelihood%20and%20dignity.%20It%20is%20time%20to%20fight%20for%2