0Goel%20was%20created%20on%20May%2015%2C%202022.%20Goel%20was%20due%20to%20retire%20from%20the%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20on%20December%2031%2C%202022%2C%20but%20he%20requested%20voluntary%20retirement%20on%20personal%20grounds%20on%20November%2018%2C%202022%2C%20and%20it%20was%20approved%20on%20the%20very%20same%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20a%20two-judge%20Bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22internal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Fsupreme-court-dismisses-pil-seeking-quashing-of-appointment-of-arun-goel-as-election-commissioner%2F%5C%22%3Edismissed%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0a%20public%20interest%20litigation%20filed%20by%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%20seeking%20to%20quash%20Goel%E2%80%99s%20appointment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20matter%20of%20practice%2C%20the%20commission%20comprises%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20and%20two%20election%20commissioners.%20Even%20before%20Goel%E2%80%99s%20resignation%2C%20there%20was%20one%20vacancy%20in%20the%20commission%20with%20the%20retirement%20of%20Anup%20Chandra%20Pandey%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdid-arun-goel-express-his-dissent-within-the-ec-e-a-s-sarma-asks-president-to-probe%5C%22%3EDid%20Arun%20Goel%20Express%20His%20Dissent%20Within%20the%20EC%3F%20E.A.S.%20Sarma%20Asks%20President%20to%20Probe%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHow%20CEC%20and%20ECs%20are%20appointed%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Article%20324(2)%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20shall%20consist%20of%20a%20CEC%20and%20such%20number%20of%20other%20ECs%2C%20if%20any%2C%20as%20the%20President%20of%20India%20may%20from%20time%20to%20time%20fix%20and%20the%20appointment%20of%20a%20CEC%20and%20other%20ECs%20shall%2C%20subject%20to%20the%20provisions%20of%20any%20law%20made%20in%20that%20behalf%20by%20the%20Parliament%2C%20be%20made%20by%20the%20President%20of%20India.%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20very%20recently%2C%20there%20was%20no%20law%20laying%20down%20the%20procedure%20for%20the%20appointment%20of%20CECs%20and%20ECs%2C%20and%20thus%20it%20was%20the%20sole%20prerogative%20of%20the%20Union%20executive%20to%20appoint%20CECs%20and%20ECs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%2C%20the%20commission%20had%20only%20a%20CEC.%20It%20was%20on%20October%2016%2C%201989%2C%20that%20the%20President%20of%20India%2C%20in%20exercise%20of%20his%20powers%20under%20Clause%202%20of%20Article%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.constitutionofindia.net%2Farticles%2Farticle-324-superintendence-direction-and-control-of-elections-to-be-vested-in-an-election-commission%2F%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E324%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20fixed%20the%20number%20of%20ECs%20as%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20on%2C%20on%20October%2016%2C%201989%2C%20V.S.%20Seigell%20and%20S.S.%20Dhanoa%20were%20appointed%20as%20ECs.%20It%20was%20for%20the%20first%20time%20after%20Independence%20that%20ECs%20were%20appointed%2C%20thereby%20making%20the%20ECI%20a%20multi-member%20commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%201%2C%201990%2C%20the%20President%20of%20India%20issued%20two%20notifications%20%E2%80%93%20one%20rescinding%2C%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20the%20notification%20of%20October%207%2C%201989%20creating%20the%20two%20posts%20of%20ECs%20and%20another%20rescinding%2C%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20the%20notification%20of%20October%2016%2C%201989%2C%20by%20which%20the%20appointment%20of%20S.S.%20Dhanoa%20and%20V.S.%20Seigell%20was%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhanao%20unsuccessfully%20challenged%20these%20two%20notifications%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmain.sci.gov.in%2Fjonew%2Fjudis%2F30335.pdf%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ES.S.%20Dhanoa%20versus%20Union%20of%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20rejected%20the%20petition%20by%20Dhanao%20holding%20that%20the%20creation%20and%20abolition%20of%20posts%20was%20the%20prerogative%20of%20the%20Executive%20and%20(in%20the%20present%20case)%20of%20the%20President%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20further%20held%20that%20Article%20324(2)%20leaves%20it%20to%20the%20President%20of%20India%20to%20fix%20and%20appoint%20such%20a%20number%20of%20ECs%20as%20he%20may%20from%20time%20to%20time%20determine.%20The%20power%20to%20create%20the%20posts%20is%20unfettered.%20So%20also%20is%20the%20power%20to%20reduce%20or%20abolish%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0Parliament%20passed%20an%20Act%20titled%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bareactslive.com%2FACA%2FACT1510.HTM%3FAspxAutoDetectCookieSupport%3D1%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChief%20Election%20Commissioner%20and%20other%20Commissioners.%20(Conditions%20of%20Service)%20Act%2C%201991%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20regulate%20conditions%20of%20service%20of%20CECs%20and%20ECs.%20The%201991%20Act%20came%20to%20be%20amended%20by%20an%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiacode.nic.in%2Frepealed-act%2Frepealed_act_documents%2FA1994-4.pdf%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOrdinance%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0published%20on%20October%201%2C%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%201%2C%201993%2C%20the%20President%20again%20issued%20a%20notification%20fixing%20the%20number%20of%20ECs%20other%20than%20the%20CEC%20at%20two%20until%20further%20orders.%20Two%20ECs%2C%C2%A0M.S.%20Gill%20and%20G.V.G.%20Krishnamurthy%2C%20were%20appointed%20with%20effect%20from