2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F1890680%2F%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ET.N.%20Seshan%2C%20Chief%20Election%20Commr.%20of%20India%20versus%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20rejected%20the%20challenge.%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fsection%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bench%20observed%20that%20the%C2%A0concept%20of%20plurality%20was%20writ%20large%20on%20the%20face%20of%20Article%20324%2C%20Clause%20(2)%20whereof%20clearly%20envisages%20a%20multi-member%20election%20commission%20comprising%20a%20CEC%20and%20one%20or%20more%20ECs.%20If%20a%20multi-member%20election%20commission%20was%20not%20contemplated%2C%20where%20was%20the%20need%20to%20provide%20in%20clause%20(3)%20for%20the%20CEC%20to%20act%20as%20its%20chairman%2C%20the%20Bench%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20no%20room%20for%20doubt%20that%20the%20ECI%20could%20be%20a%20multi-member%20body%2C%20the%20Bench%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20had%20multi-member%20election%20commissions%20in%20operation%20since%201993%2C%20with%20decision-making%20power%20by%20majority%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch4%3E%3Cb%3ESupreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20intervention%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%202%20last%20year%2C%20a%20Constitution%20Bench%20comprising%20Justices%20K.M.%20Joseph%2C%20Ajay%20Rastogi%2C%20Aniruddha%20Bose%2C%20Hrishikesh%20Roy%20and%20C.T.%20Ravikumar%20had%3Ca%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22internal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Fcollegium-for-election-commission-members-supreme-court-takes-away-governments-powers%2F%5C%22%3E%C2%A0held%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20the%20appointment%20of%20CECs%20and%20ECs%20would%20be%20on%20the%20recommendation%20of%20a%3Ca%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22internal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Fexplaining-election-commission-of-india-ruling-supreme-court-checks-executives-power-to-appoint-members-calls-for-balance%2F%5C%22%3E%C2%A0committee%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0consisting%20of%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20(CJI)%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bench%20believed%20that%20the%20ECI%20had%20to%20perform%20the%20arduous%20and%20unenviable%20task%20of%20remaining%20aloof%20from%20all%20forms%20of%20subjugation%20by%20and%20interference%20from%20the%20Executive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EParliament%20undid%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20ruling%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonths%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20ruling%2C%20the%20Parliament%20enacted%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiacode.nic.in%2Fhandle%2F123456789%2F19721%3Fview_type%3Dbrowse%26sam_handle%3D123456789%2F1362%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChief%20Election%20Commissioner%20and%20other%20Election%20Commissioners%20(Appointment%2C%20Conditions%20of%20Service%20and%20Term%20of%20Office)%20Act%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Act%20has%20dropped%20the%20CJI%20from%20the%20selection%20committee%20to%20appoint%20a%20CEC%20and%20ECs.%20The%20selection%20committee%20under%20the%20new%20law%20to%20appoint%20a%20CEC%20and%20ECs%20provides%20the%20Executive%20a%20two-third%20voting%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20also%20provides%20that%20a%20CEC%20and%20other%20ECs%20be%20appointed%20from%20amongst%20persons%20who%20are%20holding%20or%20have%20held%20a%20post%20equivalent%20to%20the%20rank%20of%20secretary%20to%20the%20government%20of%20India%20and%20who%20are%20persons%20of%20integrity%20with%20knowledge%20of%20and%20experience%20in%20the%20management%20and%20conduct%20of%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20law%2C%20the%20search%20committee%20headed%20by%20the%20minister%20of%20law%20and%20justice%20and%20comprising%20two%20other%20members%20not%20below%20the%20rank%20of%20secretary%20to%20the%20government%20of%20India%20shall%20prepare%20a%20panel%20of%20five%20persons%20for%20consideration%20of%20the%20selection%20committee%2C%20for%20appointment%20as%20a%20CEC%20and%20other%20ECs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20a%20panel%20comprising%20the%20Prime%20Minister%3B%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20a%20Union%20cabinet%20minister%20to%20be%20nominated%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20shall%20recommend%20the%20name%20for%20the%20appointment%20to%20be%20made%20by%20the%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Act%20also%20provides%20that%20a%20CEC%20and%20ECs%20shall%20hold%20office%20for%20a%20term%20of%20six%20years%20from%20the%20date%20on%20which%20they%20assume%20office%20or%20till%20they%20attain%20the%20age%20of%20sixty-five%20years%2C%20whichever%20is%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20clarifies%20that%20when%20an%20EC%20is%20appointed%20as%20the%20CEC%2C%20his%20term%20of%20office%20shall%20not%20be%20more%20than%20six%20years%20in%20aggregate.%20CECs%20and%20ECs%20shall%20not%20be%20eligible%20for%20re-appointment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch4%3E%3Cb%3EDifferent%20yardstick%20for%20removal%20of%20CEC%20and%20EC%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Article%20324(5)%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20a%20CEC%C2%A0shall%20not%20be%20removed%20from%20his%20office%20except%20in%20like%20manner%20and%20on%20the%20like%20grounds%20as%20a%20judge%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20conditions%20of%20service%20of%20a%20CEC%20shall%20not%20be%20varied%20to%20his%20disadvantage%20after%20his%20appointment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20removal%20of%20ECs%2C%20the%20Constitution%20provides%20that%20they%20shall%20not%20be%20removed%20from%20office%20except%20on%20the%20recommendation%20of%20the%20CEC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Parliament%20in%20the%202023%20Act%20also%20codified%20the%20same%20notwithstanding%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20observation%20in%20its%20March%202023%20ruling%20that%20it%20was%C2%A0desirable%20that%20the%20grounds%20of%20removal%20of%20the%20ECs%20shall%20be%20the%20same%20as%20that%20of%20the%20CEC%2C%20that%20is%2C%20on%20like%20grounds%20as%20a%20judge%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20subject%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3Erecommendation%20of%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%3C%2Fi%3E%E2%80%9D%20as%20provided%20under%20the%20second%20proviso%20to%20Article%20324(5)%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Fexplained-on-arun-goels-resignation-what-is-the-law-on-appointment-and-termination-of-services-of-election-commissioners%2F%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20first%20appeared%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Leaflet%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710156729000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Farun-goels-resignation-what-is-the-established-law-on-the-appointment-of-election-commissioners%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20had%20multi-member%20election%20commissions%20in%20operation%20since%201993%2C%20with%20decision-making%20power%20by%20majority%20vote.%20With%20Arun%20Goel's%20resignation%20as%20election%20commissioner%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20one-man%20commission.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Farun-goels-resignation-what-is-the-established-law-on-the-appointment-of-election-commissioners%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%3A%20Amid%20Threats%2C%20Over%205%2C000%20Almond%20Workers%20in%20Karawal%20Nagar%20Protest%20for%20Fair%20Wages%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11185815%2FUntitled-design-41.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWinters%20are%20gradually%20receding.%20Once%20again%2C%20the%20time-honoured%20tradition%20of%20consuming%20overnight-soaked%20almonds%20took%20centre%20stage%20in%20Indian%20breakfast%20rituals%2C%20believed%20to%20enhance%20memory%20along%20with%20many%20other%20health%20benefits.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapps.fas.usda.gov%2Fnewgainapi%2Fapi%2FReport%2FDownloadReportByFileName%3FfileName%3DTree%2BNuts%2BAnnual_New%2BDelhi_India_IN2023-0068.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECalifornia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20United%20States%20accounts%20for%20roughly%2090%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20overall%20almond%20imports.%20And%2C%20Foreign%20Agricultural%20Services%20of%20US%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%20has%20forecasted%20that%20India%20will%20import%201%2C70%2C000%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20almonds%20in%202023-24%20MY%20(market%20year).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%2C%20as%20these%20glossy-packaged%20almonds%20make%20their%20way%20from%20the%20orchards%20to%20our%20tables%2C%20they%20traverse%20a%20path%20lined%20with%20the%20toil%20and%20sweat%20of%20countless%20workers.%20Can%20those%20workers%20ever%20afford%20to%20feed%20their%20children%20the%20almonds%20they%20process%3F%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20prominent%20question%20echoing%20the%20narrow%20lanes%20of%20Karawal%20Nagar%20where%2C%20since%20March%201%2C%20more%20than%205%2C000%20workers%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20them%20women%2C%20have%20been%20protesting%20for%20an%20increase%20in%20their%20wages.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20more%20than%2050%20godowns%20in%20Karawal%20Nagar%20which%20are%20basically%20huller%2Fsheller%20facilities%20where%20the%20outer%20coverings%20of%20almonds%20are%20removed.%20The%20almonds%20are%20then%20passed%20through%20rollers%20and%20sifters%20to%20remove%20the%20fuzzy%20outer%20hull%2C%20inner%20shell%20and%20any%20debris%20from%20the%20orchard%2C%20such%20as%20sticks%20and%20rocks.%20They%20are%20also%20sorted%20depending%20on%20their%20sizes%20and%20then%20packed%20to%20be%20sold%20into%20the%20market.%20The%20livelihoods%20of%20around%20100%20families%20depend%20on%20these%20godowns.%20The%20nuts%20arrive%20from%20the%20orchards%20of%20California%20to%20the%20big%20businessmen%20operating%20from%20the%20Khari%20Baoli%20region%20of%20Delhi.%20These%20businessmen%20give%20contracts%20to%20the%20godown%20owners%20in%20Karawal%20Nagar%20to%20get%20their%20almonds%20shelled%2C%20hulled%2C%20cleaned%2C%20sorted%20and%20packed.%20And%20these%20godown%20owners%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20hire%20the%20workers%E2%80%94%20men%2C%20primarily%2C%20for%20operating%20the%20shelling%2Fhulling%20and%20packaging%20machines%2C%20and%20women%20for%20cleaning%20and%20sorting%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20godowns%20are%20located%20in%20the%20residential%20area%20of%20Karawal%20Nagar%2C%20which%20is%20different%20from%20the%20demarcated%20industrial%20area.%20None%20of%20the%20godowns%20here%20are%20licensed%20or%20legally%20operating.%20The%20basements%20of%20the%20big%20bungalows%20of%20the%20owners%20are%20used%20as%20godowns.%20Yogesh%2C%20the%20Coordinator%20of%20Karawal%20Nagar%20Mazdoor%20Union%20(KMU)%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20walk%20through%20these%20lanes%2C%20you%20cannot%20identify%20that%20a%20godown%20is%20operational%20here.%20They%20do%20not%20operate%20in%20the%20industrial%20areas%20because%2C%20however%20less%2C%20there%20are%20still%20chances%20of%20the%20labour%20department%20conducting%20inspections%20in%20those%20areas.%20Also%2C%20no%20worker%20in%20the%20industrial%20area%20will%20work%20for%20such%20lower%20wages.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlmost%20all%20the%20almond%20workers%20in%20the%20area%20have%20migrated%20from%20Bihar%20and%20belong%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Bind%E2%80%99%20caste%2C%20categorised%20as%20Other%20Backward%20Class%20(OBC)%20in%20the%20state.%20Those%20employed%20in%20the%20operating%20machines%20%E2%80%94%20mostly%20men%20%E2%80%94%20are%20paid%20Rs%205%20for%20every%20kilogram%20they%20process%20while%20those%20involved%20in%20manual%20work%20%E2%80%94%20usually%20women%20%E2%80%94%20are%20paid%20Rs%202%20for%20every%20kilogram.%20After%20interviewing%20the%20workers%2C%20we%20found%20out%20that%2C%20even%20on%20the%20luckiest%20days%2C%20they%20earn%20Rs%20300%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20minimum%20wage%20of%20673%20per%20day%20for%20an%20unskilled%20worker%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flabour.delhi.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FLabour%2Fgeneric_multiple_files%2Fadobe_scan_23-oct-2023.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%20per%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20labour%20laws.%20The%20average%20earning%20of%20these%20almond%20workers%20swings%20around%20Rs%20200%2Fday%20and%20on%20some%20days%2C%20they%20make%20as%20low%20as%20Rs%2050.%20There%20are%20no%20weekly%20offs%20and%20their%20working%20hours%20easily%20stretch%20up%20to%2014-15%20hours%2Fday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11185934%2FUntitled-design-40.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11185934%2FUntitled-design-40.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11185934%2FUntitled-design-40-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11185934%2FUntitled-design-40-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701146%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAlmond%20workers%20of%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Karawal%20Nagar%20stage%20protest%20for%20better%20wages%20and%20working%20conditions.%20Photo%3A%20Meer%20Faisal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVishal%2C%20another%20Coordinator%20from%20KMU%2C%20elaborates%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20many%20workers%20here%20who%20have%20been%20living%20in%20the%20same%20small%20and%20dingy%20room%20for%20the%20past%20two%20decades%20now%20while%20the%20godown%20owners%20have%20built%20multiple%20bungalows%2C%20have%20prospered%20from%20one%20godown%20to%20many%2C%20from%20one%20factory%20to%20many%20others.%20They%20have%20extended%20their%20businesses%20to%20the%20new%20Tronica%20City%20located%20nearby.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20will%20we%20bring%20up%20our%20children%3F%20Don%E2%80%99t%20they%20deserve%20a%20bowl%20full%20of%20rice%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGayatri%20Devi*%2C%20a%20worker%20in%20her%2050s%2C%20who%20migrated%20from%20Muzaffarpur%20district%20in%20Bihar%20around%202%20decades%20back%2C%20told%20us%2C%20%E2%80%9CAround%2020%20years%20back%2C%20when%20almonds%20were%20broken%20by%20hand%2C%20we%20used%20to%20make%20Rs%2020%20for%20breaking%20and%20sorting%20one%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekatta%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(big%20urn%20of%20around%2021-20%20kg)%20of%20almonds.%20After%20relentless%20protesting%2C%20we%20got%20it%20increased%20to%2040%20and%20then%2060%20rupees%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekatta%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Later%20on%2C%20when%20machines%20came%2C%20the%20breaking%20of%20almonds%20began%20to%20be%20done%20on%20the%20machines%20for%20which%20male%20workers%20were%20hired.%20The%20sorting%20and%20cleaning%20is%20still%20done%20manually%20and%20women%20are%20involved%20in%20this%20work.%20We%20protested%20in%202012%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20Karawal%20Nagar%20Mazdoor%20Union%20and%20got%20the%20wage%20increased%20from%20Re%201%20to%20Rs%202%2Fkg.%20The%20owners%20also%20promised%20that%20every%20year%20one%20rupee%20will%20be%20increased%20in%20our%20wages.%20But%20it%20never%20happened.%20Our%20wages%20have%20been%20stagnant%20for%20the%20past%2012%20years%20despite%20the%20rising%20prices%20of%20everything%20around%20us%20%E2%80%94%20flour%2C%20rice%2C%20pulses%2C%20vegetables%2C%20oil%2C%20and%20gas.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKusum%20Singh*%2C%20another%20worker%20who%20has%20been%20working%20in%20the%20godowns%20since%202003%2C%20told%20us%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20demanding%20that%20the%20wages%20of%20workers%20involved%20in%20sorting%20be%20increased%20to%20Rs%2012%2Fkg%20and%20the%20wages%20of%20workers%20involved%20in%20machine%20work%20be%20increased%20to%20Rs%2010%2Fkg.%E2%80%9D%20Yogesh%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20also%20demanding%20that%20the%20owners%20ensure%20that%20all%20the%20workers%20get%20their%20salaries%20within%20the%20first%205%20days%20of%20every%20month.%20And%2C%20their%20work%20hours%20should%20be%20pre-decided%20and%20fixed%20at%20not%20more%20than%208%20hours%2Fday.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGayatri%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%207%20members%20in%20my%20house.%20We%20are%20somehow%20managing%20to%20send%20our%20children%20to%20a%20government%20school%20and%20both%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%2C%20have%20been%20toiling%20day%20and%20night%20to%20make%20our%20ends%20meet.%20Two%20rupees%20per%20kg%20is%20not%20enough%20to%20sustain%20us.%20Our%20demands%20are%20very%20genuine.%20We%20are%20just%20asking%20for%20our%20rights%20%E2%80%94%20the%20due%20payment%20of%20our%20labour.%E2%80%9D%20She%20asks%2C%20%E2%80%9CHow%20will%20we%20bring%20up%20our%20children%3F%20Don%E2%80%99t%20they%20deserve%20a%20bowl%20full%20of%20rice%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20asked%20Anita%20Devi*%2C%20who%20has%20been%20working%20in%20almond%20godowns%20for%2015%20years%20now%2C%20about%20how%20she%20manages%20at%20such%20low%20wages%2C%20she%20sadly%20smiles%2C%20%E2%80%9CSome%20days%20we%20eat%202%20rotis.%20On%20most%20days%2C%20we%20survive%20on%20just%20one.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESunil%20Kumar*%2C%20a%20worker%20in%20his%20late%2030s%2C%20operates%20the%20machines%20which%20are%20used%20to%20break%20the%20almond%20shells.%20All%20the%20five%20members%20of%20his%20family%20work%20in%20these%20godowns.%20He%20told%20us%2C%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%2C%20the%20owner%20calls%20us%20at%2012%20at%20night%2C%20sometimes%2C%20at%204%20in%20the%20morning.There%20are%20times%20when%20we%20sat%20down%20to%20eat%20and%20we%20were%20called%20so%2C%20we%20had%20to%20skip%20meals%20and%20rush%20to%20the%20godown.%20If%20we%20delay%20even%20once%2C%20the%20owner%20threatens%20to%20fire%20us.%20There%20are%20times%20when%20we%20have%20spent%202-3%20consecutive%20days%20working%20in%20the%20godown.%E2%80%9D%20He%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20we%20began%20the%20protest%2C%20the%20owner%20has%20held%20our%20last%20month%E2%80%99s%20wages.%20When%20we%20go%20ask%20for%20it%2C%20he%20says%20%E2%80%94%20Come%20back%20to%20work.%20You%20will%20be%20paid%20last%20month%E2%80%99s%20wages%2C%20only%20if%20you%20come%20back%20to%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERam%20Kumar*%20is%20a%2020-year-old%20man%20whose%20family%20migrated%20from%20Nalanda%2C%20Bihar%20when%20he%20was%20child.%20He%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20began%20working%20in%20these%20godowns%20at%20the%20age%20of%2010.%20The%20wages%20have%20been%20the%20same%20ever%20since%20I%20joined.%20But%20the%20room%20rent%3F%20They%20have%20increased%20from%20150-200%20rupees%20to%202000-2500%20rupees%20per%20month.%20Every%20month%2C%20I%20earn%20only%206-7%20thousand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20March%201%2C%20these%20workers%20held%20a%20rally%2C%20presenting%20a%20collective%20demand%20to%20the%20owners%20%E2%80%94%20increase%20in%20wages.%20Following%20a%20lack%20of%20response%20to%20their%20appeal%2C%20they%20initiated%20the%20protest.%20Subsequently%2C%20on%20March%203rd%2C%20they%20submitted%20a%20formal%20memorandum%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20delineating%20their%20grievances%20and%20seeking%20intervention.%20Communications%20were%20also%20dispatched%20to%20key%20authorities%20within%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20including%20the%C2%A0%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20the%20Labour%20Minister%20and%20the%20Labour%20Court%2C%20requesting%20for%20attention%20to%20their%20concerns.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20the%20workers%20in%20the%20area%20have%20stopped%20going%20to%20work%2C%20as%20a%20result%20all%20the%20godowns%20have%20been%20shut%20for%20the%20past%2010%20days%20now.%20Losing%20the%20wages%20for%20these%20days%2C%20is%20affecting%20the%20already%20impoverished%20workers%20despite%20of%20which%20they%20are%20determined%20in%20their%20resolve%20to%20continue%20the%20strike.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%201-2%20years%2C%20a%20worker%20dies%20of%20serious%20health%20issues%20like%20respiratory%20problems%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESunil%E2%80%99s%20words%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20dismal%20working%20conditions%20of%20these%20workers%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20we%20shell%20the%20almonds%2C%20huge%20amounts%20of%20sawdust%20comes%20out%20of%20the%20machines.%20The%20working%20conditions%20are%20such%20that%20the%20owner%20cannot%20even%20bear%20to%20stand%20near%20those%20machines.%20Not%20even%20for%20a%20minute.%E2%80%9D%20Yogesh%20highlights%2C%20%E2%80%9CBecause%20of%20the%20sawdust%2C%20every%201-2%20years%2C%20a%20worker%20dies%20of%20serious%20health%20issues%20like%20respiratory%20problems.%20The%20sawdust%20and%20scobs%20of%20the%20shells%20enter%20their%20system.%20A%20few%20years%20back%20a%2030-35%20year%20old%20man%20fell%20seriously%20ill.%20We%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20cough%20or%20TB%2C%20but%20later%20the%20doctors%20found%20out%20there%20was%20sawdust%20inside%20his%20body.%20He%20died%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20proper%20treatment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESafolite%2C%20which%20is%20the%20sodium%20salt%20of%20hydroxymethanesulphinic%20acid%2C%20is%20used%20to%20bleach%20the%20almonds%20and%20make%20them%20look%20fresh.%20Safolite%20is%20commonly%20used%20in%20industries%20as%20discharge%20agent%20in%20textile%20printing%2C%20as%20redox%20catalyst%20in%20polymerisation%20process%20for%20manufacturing%20polymer%2Fsynthetic%20rubber.%20According%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.transpek-silox.com%2Fen%2Fnewpdf%2F3_TSIPL_MSDS_SFS_Final_2018.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Material%20Safety%20Data%20Sheet%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20printed%20by%20the%20Silox%20India%20%E2%80%94%20the%20primary%20manufacturer%20of%20this%20chemical%E2%80%94%2C%20Safolite%20%E2%80%9Ccauses%20skin%20irritation%2C%20serious%20eye%20irritation%2C%20may%20cause%20respiratory%20irritation%2C%20and%20is%20suspected%20of%20causing%20genetic%20defect%20and%20damaging%20the%20unborn%20child%20(If%20exposed).%E2%80%9D%20Under%20the%20%E2%80%98Precautionary%20statements%20(Prevention)%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20company%20documents%20mentions%2C%20%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20handle%20until%20all%20safety%20precautions%20have%20been%20read%20and%20understood%2C%20Avoid%20breathing%20dust%20%2F%20fume%20%2F%20mist%20%2F%20vapours%20%2F%20spray%2C%20Use%20only%20outdoors%20or%20in%20a%20well-ventilated%20area%2C%20Wear%20protective%20gloves%2Fprotective%20clothing%2Feye%20protection%2Fface%20protection.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESunil%20laments%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20operate%20the%20machine%20today%2C%20my%20spit%20and%20cough%20will%20remain%20infected%20with%20the%20chemical%20for%20around%20a%20week.%20The%20owner%20lives%20and%20eats%20in%20peace.%20And%20our%20lifespan%20is%20decreasing%20because%20of%20inhaling%20that%20hazardous%20chemical.%20Despite%20knowing%20that%2C%20we%20continue%20to%20work%20because%20we%20are%20helpless.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20other%20option.%20If%20any%20of%20us%20gets%20a%20proper%20medical%20check-up%2C%20tens%20of%20diseases%20and%20ailments%20will%20be%20diagnosed%E2%80%A6such%20hazardous%20are%20our%20working%20conditions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGayatri%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20the%20owners%20made%20us%20use%20acid%20to%20soften%20the%20almond%20shells.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20our%20hands%20were%20always%20bruised%20and%20sometimes%2C%20even%20bled.%20These%20days%20there%20is%20constant%20itching%20and%20other%20skin%20diseases%20in%20our%20hands%20because%20of%20the%20chemicals%20used%20in%20various%20processes.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20of%20these%20godowns%20are%20illegal%20and%20operating%20from%20residential%20areas%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYogesh%2C%20while%20revealing%20the%20names%20of%20some%20owners%20%E2%80%94%20Rakesh%20Mishra%2C%20Pramod%2C%20Vasudev%20Mishra%2C%20Manoj%2C%20Shankar%2C%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20Sunil%2C%20Bablu%2C%20Sandeep%2C%20Kailash%2C%20Sachin%2C%20Indraj%2C%20Uttam%20singh%2C%20Parmod%2C%20Vishnu%20and%20Pappu%20%E2%80%94%20told%20us%2C%20%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20them%20enjoy%20support%20from%20local%20BJP%20MLA%20Mohan%20Singh%20Bisht%20and%20Nigam%20Parshad%20Satyapal%20Singh.%20In%20fact%2C%20one%20of%20the%20godown%20owners%20%E2%80%94%20Vasudev%20Mishra%20%E2%80%94%20even%20stood%20for%20Nigam%20Parshad%20elections%20and%20enjoyed%20the%20support%20of%20Bisht.%20But%2C%20later%2C%20instead%20of%20him%2C%20Satyapal%20was%20made%20the%20Parshad.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20all%20of%20these%20godowns%20are%20illegal%20and%20operating%20from%20residential%20areas%2C%20the%20owners%20give%20huge%20funds%20to%20the%20MLA%20and%20regularly%20bribe%20the%20local%20policemen%20to%20be%20able%20to%20operate%20these%20illegal%20godowns.%20In%20some%20of%20the%20godowns%2C%20even%20children%20as%20small%20as%206-8-year-olds%20are%20working%20as%20labourers.%20There%20have%20been%20occasional%20complaints%20against%20this.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20the%20owners%20hide%20the%20children.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20labourers%20of%20Karawal%20Nagar%20are%20Zindabad%E2%80%A6%20Won%E2%80%99t%20let%20someone%20steal%20our%20labour%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVishal%20explains%20the%20attempts%20to%20halt%20the%20protest%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20the%20local%20police%20tried%20to%20stop%20our%20protests.%20But%20we%20told%20them%20that%20this%20is%20a%20labour%20dispute%20and%20we%20are%20carrying%20out%20peaceful%20rallies%20and%20not%20breaking%20any%20laws.%20After%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20went%20futile%2C%20the%20godown%20owners%20took%20the%20lumpen%20hooligans%20in%20the%20area%20to%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Etheka%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20gave%20them%20liquor.%20After%20the%20boys%20became%20drunk%2C%20they%20were%20supplied%20with%20batons%20and%20sticks%20to%20go%20into%20the%20area%20and%20beat%20workers.%20It%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20aggravate%20workers%20to%20retaliate%20and%20then%20the%20police%20would%20arrest%20them%20and%20the%20protest%20would%20break.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20owner%20threatens%20us%20%E2%80%94%20You%20will%20die%20on%20the%20road%20starving%20and%20will%20not%20get%20any%20more%20work.%20They%20are%20trying%20to%20aggravate%20us%20against%20the%20activists%20who%20have%20been%20helping%20us.%E2%80%9D%20tells%20Anita.%20To%20this%2C%20Gayatri%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20mill%20owners%20are%20not%20interested%20in%20any%20dialogue%20with%20us.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20allow%20any%20communication%2C%20instead%2C%20are%20threatening%20us%20that%20they%20would%20shift%20the%20godown%20to%20someplace%20else%20where%20they%20would%20get%20labourers%20for%20a%20cheaper%20rate%20%E2%80%94%20perhaps%20at%201%20rupee%20or%201%20rupee%2050%20paise.%20We%20dare%20them%20to%20do%20that.%20The%20labourers%20of%20Karawal%20Nagar%20are%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EZindabad%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20We%20will%20work%20anywhere%20else%20to%20earn%20our%20daily%20bread%20but%20won%E2%80%99t%20let%20someone%20steal%20our%20labour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20owners%20are%20pasting%20posters%20all%20over%20the%20area%20saying%20that%20the%20wages%20given%20to%20almond%20workers%20in%20Delhi%20are%20higher%20than%20other%20states.%20Rakesh%2C%20another%20activist%20from%20KMU%2C%20told%20us%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20lie%20which%20we%20have%20busted.%20We%20have%20found%20out%20from%20the%20activists%20in%20other%20states.%20In%20Mumbai%2C%20Jaipur%20and%20many%20other%20cities%20the%20wages%20are%20higher.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYogesh%20narrated%2C%20%E2%80%9CLast%20night%2C%20some%20owners%20were%20forcing%20a%20few%20women%20workers%20to%20work.%20When%20the%20other%20women%20found%20out%2C%20they%20went%20to%20the%20godown%20and%20protested.%20The%20owners%20had%20already%20brought%20in%20hooligans%20which%20then%20manhandled%20the%20women%2C%20slapped%20and%20beat%20many%20of%20them.%20When%20this%20happened%2C%20the%20SHO%20of%20the%20area%20called%20me%20and%20accused%20me%20of%20the%20violence%20against%20the%20women.%20When%20my%20lawyer%20talked%20to%20him%20and%20asserted%20that%20I%20was%20not%20even%20present%20on%20the%20spot%2C%20the%20SHO%20backed%20down.%20The%20injured%20women%2C%20later%2C%20called%20112%20to%20lodge%20a%20complaint.%20On%20the%20morning%20of%20March%2010%2C%20the%20women%20and%20the%20activists%20went%20to%20the%20DCP%2C%20North%20East%20Delhi%3B%20ACP%2C%20Khajuri%20Khas%20Police%20Station%20and%20SHO%2C%20Karawal%20Nagar%20Police%20Station%20to%20lodge%20a%20complaint.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20complaint%20mentions%20that%20the%20godown%20owners%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20Sunil%2C%20Bablu%20and%20Sandeep%2C%20along%20with%20the%20drunk%20hooligans%20attacked%20the%20women%20with%20lathis%20and%20sticks%2C%20%E2%80%9Ctore%20women%E2%80%99s%20clothes%2C%20pulled%20their%20hair%2C%20made%20casteist%20remarks%2C%20abused%20and%20molested%20them.%E2%80%9D%20It%20is%20undersigned%20by%20almond%20workers%20%E2%80%94%20Chandra%20Kumari%20(16)%2C%20Shanti%20Devi%20(37)%2C%20Urmila%20Devi%20(35)%2C%20Nishu%20(18)%2C%20Rinku%20Devi%20(36)%20and%20Rinku%20Sinha%20(32).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbout%20the%20violence%20and%20threats%20of%20the%20owners%2C%20Sunil%20comments%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20threatening%20us%20only%20to%20break%20our%20spirit%2C%20our%20protest%20and%20force%20us%20to%20go%20back%20to%20work.%20They%20say%20%E2%80%94%20Either%20come%20to%20work%20or%20go%20back%20to%20Bihar.%E2%80%9D%20He%20questions%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20working%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20our%20lives.%20And%20even%20in%20return%20for%20our%20lives%2C%20we%20are%20not%20getting%20minimum%20wage.%20How%20is%20that%20fair%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E*The%20names%20of%20all%20the%20workers%20have%20been%20changed%20to%20protect%20their%20identities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710154766000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08141416%2FScreenshot-2024-02-08-