ussia%20has%20won%20and%20taken%2040%25%20of%20Ukrainian%20territory%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20managed%20to%20gain%20my%20trust%20and%20rushed%20me%20into%20the%20decision%20by%20saying%20that%20only%20ten%20vacancies%20are%20available%20for%20this%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20team%20asked%20me%20to%20deposit%20Rs%203%20lakh%20as%20%E2%80%98service%20charge%E2%80%99%20for%20assisting%20me%20with%20a%20visa%2C%20flights%20and%20getting%20me%20to%20the%20Russian%20Army%20facility%20in%20Moscow.%20I%20somehow%20arranged%20the%20money%20with%20my%20mother%E2%80%99s%20savings%20and%20borrowed%20some%20money%20from%20my%20brother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELittle%20did%20I%20know%20that%20I%20was%20walking%20into%20a%20death%20trap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20trap%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20asked%20to%20land%20in%20Chennai%20in%20December%20last%20year%20where%20I%20met%20nine%20more%20men%2C%20most%20of%20them%20in%20their%2020s%2C%20who%20were%20also%20due%20to%20go%20to%20Russia%20for%20the%20same%20job%20of%20a%20helper%20with%20the%20Russian%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20about%20ten%20days%2C%20we%20stayed%20at%20a%20hotel%20waiting%20for%20the%20flight%20tickets%20to%20be%20booked%20by%20Baba%E2%80%99s%20team.%20I%20met%20Hamil%20%E2%80%93%20a%2026-year-old%20man%20from%20Gujarat%20%E2%80%93%20who%20was%20a%20very%20kind%20person%20at%20heart.%20We%20instantly%20became%20friends%20and%20spent%20time%20sharing%20our%20dreams%20and%20hopes%20from%20life.%20He%20wanted%20to%20do%20well%20in%20life%20and%20make%20his%20parents%20proud%20by%20landing%20a%20job%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamil%20was%20sent%20to%20Russia%20six%20days%20ahead%20of%20me%2C%20with%20five%20other%20men.%20On%20December%2022%20it%20was%20my%20turn%20to%20go%20with%20the%20remaining%20men.%20We%20flew%20from%20Chennai%20to%20Moscow%20via%20Bahrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20landed%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20Baba%E2%80%99s%20accomplice%20Nigel%20came%20to%20receive%20us.%20He%20introduced%20himself%20as%20a%20doctor%20in%20the%20Russian%20Army.%20I%20noticed%20that%20all%20bags%20were%20being%20scanned%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20except%20ours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20kept%20in%20a%20room%20in%20Moscow%20city%20for%20a%20few%20days%2C%20where%20we%20met%20Moin%20and%20Ramesh%20who%20were%20Baba%E2%80%99s%20partners.%20They%20both%20had%20Russian%20citizenship.%20Moin%20told%20us%20that%20we%20are%20lucky%20to%20have%20landed%20this%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaba%20had%20told%20us%20that%20our%20monthly%20salary%20would%20be%20Rs%2040%2C000%20per%20month%20and%20could%20stretch%20up%20to%20Rs%2060%2C000%20if%20we%20work%20overtime.%20But%20Moin%20told%20us%20that%20he%20has%20done%20%E2%80%98setting%E2%80%99%20with%20Russian%20Army%20officials%20to%20pay%20us%20Rs%202%2C00%2C000%20as%20monthly%20salary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20stunned.%20But%20there%20was%20a%20price%20attached%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98favour%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asked%20us%20to%20give%20him%20Rs%202%20lakh%20from%20our%20first%20salary.%20We%20agreed%20as%20the%20prospect%20of%20a%20great%20pay%20after%20the%20first%20month%20was%20too%20enticing%20to%20be%20ignored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11115444%2FSarfaraz2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11115444%2FSarfaraz2.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11115444%2FSarfaraz2-300x139.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11115444%2FSarfaraz2-1024x474.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701055%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22556%5C%22