n%20any%20army%20raise%20a%20soldier%20with%20just%2015%20days%20of%20training%3F%20It%20takes%20years%20for%20a%20man%20to%20be%20trained%20for%20a%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20me%20to%20run%20away%20from%20the%20camp%20in%20Ryazan%20while%20I%20still%20had%20a%20chance.%20He%20told%20me%20to%20go%20back%20to%20India%20and%20tell%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20rescue%20him%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20few%20weeks%2C%20Hamil%20died%20in%20a%20drone%20strike%20that%20landed%20on%20his%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20escape%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Moin%20started%20harassing%20us%20for%20money%20and%20asked%20us%20to%20send%20our%20ATM%20card%20details%20so%20he%20could%20withdraw%20our%20first%20salaries%20from%20our%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20received%20my%20salary.%20He%20started%20threatening%20to%20harm%20my%20family%20back%20home%20as%20he%20had%20my%20Aadhaar%20card%20details%20with%20my%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaught%20between%20a%20rock%20and%20a%20hard%20place%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20flee%20the%20Russian%20army%20camp%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20474px)%2085vw%2C%20474px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11120416%2FSarfaraz5.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22474%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11120416%2FSarfaraz5.jpg%20811w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11120416%2FSarfaraz5-203x300.jpg%20203w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11120416%2FSarfaraz5-692x1024.jpg%20692w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701061%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22701%5C%22%3EOne%20day%2C%20I%20went%20out%20of%20the%20army%20facility%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20buying%20snacks%20from%20the%20supermarket.%20The%20security%20guard%2