shes%20to%20encourage%20other%20women%20like%20her.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20Thursday%2C%20I%20move%20all%20my%20furniture%20aside%20to%20keep%20all%20the%20fruits%20for%20packaging.%20My%20young%20children%20also%20pitch%20in%20to%20deliver%20orders%20on%20their%20bicycles%20and%20earn%20Rs%205-10%20per%20delivery.%20With%20this%2C%20my%20children%20are%20also%20learning%20the%20basics%20of%20entrepreneurship%2C%20the%20value%20of%20money%2C%20and%20above%20all%20importance%20of%20inclusive%20growth%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERashi%20continues%20to%20inform%20that%20every%20Thursday%2C%20she%20pitches%20in%20the%20household%20chores%20so%20that%20Priya%20has%20time%20to%20cater%20to%20all%20the%20orders.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20not%20been%20a%20single%20day%20when%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20received%20hot%20food.%20Priya%20makes%20sure%20that%20this%20work%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20affect%20household%20duties.%20Earlier%2C%20we%20would%20worry%20about%20how%20they%E2%80%99ll%20fend%20for%20themselves%20when%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20savings.%20But%20today%2C%20I%20take%20pride%20that%20Priya%20has%20earned%20financial%20freedom%20as%20well%20as%20popularity.%20She%20is%20so%20enthusiastic%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20house%20helps%20have%20aspirations%20beyond%20our%20kitchen%20and%20homes.%20If%20we%20just%20recognise%20them%20and%20give%20them%20that%20little%20push%2C%20then%20the%20sky%20is%20the%20limit.%20We%20just%20need%20to%20act%20as%20a%20small%20catalyst%20in%20helping%20such%20women%20achieve%20their%20aspirations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Priya%20says%20she%20has%20not%20only%20learnt%20to%20set%20up%20the%20small%20business%20but%20also%20to%20ensure%20a%20sustainable%20financial%20future%20for%20her%20family.%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20I%20get%20big%20profits%2C%20I%20deposit%20all%20my%20money.%20With%20this