%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELadakh%20is%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaramjeet%E2%80%99s%20family%20has%20established%20roots%20in%20Kargil%20for%20over%20five%20generations.%20Their%20home%20today%20lies%20in%20Balti%20Bazaar%2C%20which%20is%20situated%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F271231%2Fstanzin-saldon-shifah-kargil-gender-equality-public-school-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKargil%20town%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20initial%20move%20to%20Ladakh%20was%20made%20by%20my%20great-great-grandfather%2C%20who%20migrated%20from%20Mirpur%20(now%20in%20Pakistan)%20for%20trade.%20He%20settled%20in%20Kargil%20after%20marrying%20a%20woman%20hailing%20from%20a%20Buddhist%20family%20in%20Shargole%2C%20Kargil.%20In%20our%20small%20and%20tight-knit%20Sikh%20community%20in%20Kargil%2C%20familial%20ties%20are%20strong.%20There%20are%20barely%2050%20of%20us%20but%20we%20are%20engaged%20in%20various%20occupations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1080%2F14631369.2023.2236040%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520rural%2520population%2520in%2520Kargil%2Caround%2520360%2520Sikhs%252C%2520in%2520town.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Malvika%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20notes%20in%20%E2%80%98Partition%2C%20identity%20and%20belonging%20among%20Sikhs%20in%20the%20borderland%20district%20of%20Kargil%2C%20Ladakh%E2%80%99%2C%20for%20Asian%20Ethnicity%2C%20%E2%80%9CSikhs%20in%20Ladakh%20arrived%20as%20traders%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20settled%20around%20the%20major%20trading%20centres%20along%20the%20silk-route%20such%20as%20Skardu%2C%20Kargil%2C%20Leh%20in%20the%20then%20undivided%20erstwhile%20princely%20state%20as%20it%20existed%20before%201947-partition.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20ot